hadiths[282]{hadithnumber,text}:
2759,"Hazrat Miqdam bin Maadikarb (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kisi shakhs ne apni haath ki kamai se ziyada behtar khana kabhi nahin khaya, aur Allah ke Nabi Dawud (Alaihissalam) apney haathon ki kamai se khaya kartey they.'' Bukhari."
2760,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''be-shak Allah paak hai aur wo sirf paak chiz hi qubul farmata hai, aur Allah Taala ne jis chiz ke mutalliq Rasulon ko hukm farmaya , usi chiz ke mutalliq mominon ko hukm farmaya to farmaya : ''Rasulon ki jamaat ! pakizah chizen khaao aur nek amal karo.'' aur Allah Taala ne farmaya : ''emaan walo ! ham ne jo pakizah chizen tumhen ata ki hain un mein se khaao.'' phir aapney us aadmi ka zikr farmaya jo door daraz ka safar tey karta hai bikhre hue baal aur khaak aalud hai, aasman ki taraf apney haath phelaey dua karta hai : rab ji ! halanke uska khana haram , uska peena haram , uska libas haram aur usey haram ki ghiza di gaee to aisey shakhs ki dua kaisey qubul ho?'' rawahu Muslim."
2761,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''logon par eik aisa zamana aaeyga ke aadmi is baat ki parwah nahin kerega ke wo halal tareeqey se kama raha hai ya haram tareeqey se.'' Bukhari."
2762,"Hazrat Noman bin Bashir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''halal wazeh hai aur haram bhi wazeh hai, jabkey un dono ke darmiyan kuchh chizen  shak mein hain. bahut se log unhen nahin jantey , isliye jo shakhs shub'haat se bach gaya to usney apney Deen aur apni izzat ko bacha liya , aur jo shakhs shub'haat mein mubtala ho gaya to wo haram mein mubtala ho gaya, jaisey wo charwaahaa jo charaagaah ke Aas paas charaataa hai, to qarib hai ke wo us (charaagaah) mein charaaey ga , sun lo ! be-shak her badshah ki eik charaagaah hoti hai, sun lo ! be-shak Allah ki charaagaah uski haram karda chizen hain : sun lo ! jism main eik loathra hai, jab wo durust ho jata hai to sara jism durust ho jata hai, aur jab wo kharab ho jata hai to sara jism kharab ho jata hai, yad rakho ! wo dil hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
2763,"Hazrat Raafe bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kuttey ki qeemat , zaaniya ki ujrat aur pachhney laganey waley ki kamai khabees hai.'' rawahu Muslim."
2764,"Hazrat Abu-Masood Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne kuttey ki qeemat , zaaniya ki ujrat aur kaahin ki sheerni (yani niyaz) se mana farmaya hai. muttafaq aleh."
2765,"Hazrat Abu-Juhaifa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne khoon ki qeemat , kuttey ki qeemat aur zaaniya ki kamai se mana farmaya, aur sood khaney waley, khilaney waley, jism godne wali aur gudwaaney wali aur musawwir par lanat farmaee. Bukhari."
2766,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney Fateh Makka ke saal Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko Makka mein farmatey huey suna : ''be-shak Allah aur uskey Rasool ne sharab, murdar, khinzir aur buton ki khareed aur farokht ko haram qarar diya hai.'' arz kiya gaya, Allah ke Rasool ! murdar ki charbi ke barey mein bataeyn? kyonkey uskey zariey kashtiyon ko raughan kiya jata hai, khaalen chikni ki jati hain, aur log usey chiraghon mein jala kar roshni hasil kartey hain? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''nahin, wo haram hai.'' phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah yahood ko gharat karey, kyonkey Allah ne jab uski charbi haram qarar di to unhoney pighla kar bechaa aur phir uski qeemat khai.'' muttafaq aleh."
2767,Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah yahood ko gharat karey un par (murdar ki) charbi haram ki gaee to unhoney usey pighla kar farokht kiya.'' muttafaq aleh.
2768,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne kuttey aur billi ki qeemat se mana farmaya hai. rawahu Muslim.
2769,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Abu-Taiba ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko pachhney lagaey to aapney usey eik saa (taqreeban dhaai-kilo) khajuren deney aur uskey malikon ko uskey Khiraaj  mein kami karney ka hukm farmaya. muttafaq aleh."
2770,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''apni kamai se khana sab se pakizah khana hai, aur tumhari aulad bhi tumhari kamai mein se hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi, Nasai, ibne-Maja, Abu-Dawood aur Darmi . Abu-Dawood aur Darmi ki riwayat mein hai : ''aadmi ka apni kamai se khana sab se pakizah khana hai, aur be-shak uski aulad bhi uski kamai hai.''"
2771,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar koi shakhs haram maal khata hai aur phir us se sadqa karta hai to wo uski taraf se qubul nahin hota, aur wo is mein se jo kharch karta hai to is mein barkat nahin ki jati , aur agar wo usey tarka mein chhod jata hai to wo uskey liye aag mein izaafey ka baais banta hai, kyonkey Allah burai ke zariey burai khatam nahin karta balke wo neki ke zariey burai khatam karta hai aur khabees , khabees ko khatam nahin karta.'' Ahmed, Sharahus-sunnah mein bhi isi tarah hai. rawahu Ahmed."
2772,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''haram se parwarish paney wala gosht, jannat mein dakhil nahin hoga, aur haram se parwarish paney wala her gosht jahannam ki aag hi uski ziyada haq daar hai.'' (rawahu Ahmed, Darmi aur al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan)."
2773,"Hazrat Hasan bin Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se yad kiya : ''jo chiz tujhey shak mein dal dey usey chhod dey aur shak se paak chiz ikhtiyar kar , kyonkey sachchai mein itminan hai aur jhoot mein shak hai.'' Ahmed, Tirmizi, Nasai. aur Imam Darmi ne is hadees ka pehla hissey riwayat kiya hai. rawahu Ahmed  ,Tirmizi, Nasai aur Darmi."
2774,"Hazrat Wabisa bin Maabad (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Wabisa ! tum neki aur gunah ki tareef poochhney aaye ho?'' maine arz kiya, ji haan , raawi bayan kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apni ungliyan ikhatti kin aur merey seeney par haath maartay huey farmaya : ''apney nafs se poochho, apney dil se poochho.'' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne teen baar farmaya. aur phir farmaya : ''neki wo hai jis par nafs aur dil mutmain ho jaey, jabkey gunah ye hai ke wo terey nafs mein khatkey aur dil mein tardeed paida karey agar-che log tujhey fatwa den.'' rawahu Ahmed aur Darmi."
2775,"Hazrat Atiya Sa'di (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''banda haqeeqi muttaqi tab banta hai ke wo qabile-aetraz chizon ko chhodney ke sath sath aisi chizen bhi chhodey jin par koi aetraz nahin.'' rawahu Tirmizi aur ibne-Maja."
2776,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne sharab se mutalliq das qism ke afrad par lanat farmaee : uskey bananey waley, uskey banwane waley, uskey peeney waley, usey uthaney waley, jiskey paas ley jaai jaey, uskey pilaney waley, usey bechney waley, uski qeemat khaney waley, usey kharidney waley aur jis ke liye khareedi jaey. rawahu Tirmizi aur ibne-Maja."
2777,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ne sharab par, uskey peeney waley, uskey pilaney waley, uskey bechney waley, uskey kharidney waley, uskey bananey waley, jis ke liye banai jaey us par, usey lekar janey waley aur jis ke liye lekar jaai jaey, un sab par lanat farmaey.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood aur ibne-Maja."
2778,"Hazrat Muhayyisa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney pachhney laganey wali ki ujrat ke barey mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se ijazat talab ki to aapney unhen mana farma diya, wo aap se musalsal ijazat talab kartey rahey yahan tak ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usey apney oont ko khila diya kar aur usey ghulam ko khila diya kar.'' rawahu Malik, Tirmizi, Abu-Dawood aur ibne-Maja."
2779,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne kuttey ki qeemat aur gaaney wali (gulukaara ya zaaniya) ki kamai se mana farmaya hai. (rawahu al-baghwi fi Sharahus-sunnah)."
2780,"Hazrat Abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''gaaney waaliyon ko becho na unhen kharido aur na hi unhen tarbiyat do, aur unki qeemat haram hai. aisey masayel ke mutalliq ye hukm nazil hua : ''baaz log aisey bhi hain jo behuda baaten khareedtey hain.'' Ahmed, Tirmizi, ibne-Maja aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. aur Ali bin Yazid, raawi hadees mein zaeef hai. rawahu Tirmizi aur ibne-Maja . aur ham Jabir se marwi (bayan) hadees : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne billi khaney se mana farmaya. insha-Allah taala baab (silsile) (ما یحل اکلہ) mein zikr karengey."
2781,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''faraaiz ke baad halal kamaee ki talash bhi farz hai.'' (rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan)."
2782,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke un se Quran karim ki kitaabat ki ujrat ke barey mein masla puchha gaya to unhoney farmaya : koi harj nahin, wo to (huroof ke) musawwir hi hain, aur wo apney haathon ki kamai hi khatey hain. rawahu Rizeen."
2783,"Hazrat Raafe bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, arz kiya gaya, Allah ke Rasool ! kon sa kamaai sab se pakizah hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aadmi ka apney haath se kaam karna aur her achi tijarat.'' rawahu Ahmed."
2784,"Hazrat Abu-Bakar bin Abu-Maryam bayan kartey hain, Miqdam bin Maadikarb (Raziallahu anhu) ki eik londi doodh bechaa karti thi aur Miqdam (Raziallahu anhu) uski qeemat wasul kartey they, un se kaha gaya, Subhanallah ! kya wo doodh bechti hai aur tum uski qeemat wasul kartey ho? unhoney kaha : ji haan, is mein koi harj nahin, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''logon par aisa waqt bhi aaeyga jis mein dirham aur Dinar hi unhen faeyda pahunchaeyga.'' rawahu Ahmed ."
2785,"Hazrat Naafe bayan kartey hain, main Sham aur Misr ki taraf samane-tijarat bheja karta tha, chunanche ab maine Iraq ki taraf saman bhejney ki tayyari ki to main Ummul-momenin Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke paas aaya aur un se arz kiya, Ummul-momenin ! main Sham ki taraf samane-tijarat bheja karta tha, lekin ab maine Iraq ke liye tayyari ki hai, unhoney farmaya : aisey na karo, tumharey tijaarati markaz ko kya hua? kyonkey maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''jab Allah Taala kisi shakhs ki rozi ka koi sabab banaey to wo usey na chhodey jab tak ke (fayda na hone ki wajeh sey) is mein tabdili samne na aaee ho ya usey usmein nuqsan honey lagey.'' rawahu Ahmed aur ibne-Maja."
2786,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ka eik ghulam tha, wo aap ko khiraaj diya karta tha, aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) uskey khiraaj mein se khaya kartey they, eik roz wo kuchh lekar aaya to Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne is mein se khaya. ghulam ne aap se kaha : kya aap jantey hain ke ye kya tha? to Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : wo kya tha? usney kaha : main jahiliyat main eik insan ke liye kahaanat kiya karta tha, halanke mujhey kahaanat nahin aati thi, maine to usey sirf dhoka hi diya tha, wo mujhey mila hai to usney mujhey ye ata kiya hai jis mein se aapney khaya hai, wo bayan karti hain, Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne apna haath (munh mein) dala aur pet ki her chiz qai kar dali. Bukhari."
2787,Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''haram se parwarish paney wala jism jannat mein nahin jaeyga.'' (rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan).
2788,"Hazrat Zaid bin Aslam (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne doodh piya aur unhen khushgawar mehsus hua. jis shakhs ne doodh pilaya tha us se puchha ke to ne ye doodh kahan se hasil kya? usney bataya ke wo eik taalaab par gaya jis ka usney naam liya. wahan Zakat ke oont they jin ko wo pani pila rahey they, unhoney mujhey bhi unka doodh dho kar diya maine doodh ko apney mishkeezey mein dal liya ye wo doodh tha. ye sun kar Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne apna haath munh mein dala aur doodh ki qai kar di. (rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan)."
2789,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jo shakhs das dirham mein koi kapda khareedey aur un main eik dirham haram ka ho to jab tak wo kapda is par rehta hai to Allah Taala uski Namaz qubul nahin karta, phir unhoney apni do ungliyan apney dono kanon mein dal kar farmaya : agar maine ye hadees Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey na suni ho to ye dono (kaan) behrey ho jaeyn . Ahmed, Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan. aur farmaya : iski sanad zaeef hain. (rawahu Ahmed aur al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan)."
2790,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah us aadmi par rehem farmaai jo bechtey , khareedtey aur taqaza kartey waqt narmi aur kushada dili ka muzahira karey.'' Bukhari."
2791,"Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum se pehley zamaney main eik aadmi tha, farishta uski rooh qabz karney ke liye uskey paas aaya to us se puchha gaya : kya tum ne koi neki ka kaam kiya hai? usney kaha : mujhey pata nahin, phir usey kaha gaya : dekh lo usney kaha : mujhey iskey ilawa to koi aur baat yad nahin ke main duniya mein logon ke sath khareed-farokht kiya karta tha, aur main un se achhey andaz se taqaza kiya karta tha, main maal daar shakhs ko mohlat dey deta tha jabkey tangdast ko wesay hi maaf kar diya karta tha, Allah Taala ne usey jannat mein dakhil farma diya.'' muttafaq aleh."
2792,"Aur Sahih Muslim ki riwayat bhi isi tarah hai jo ke Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) aur Abu-Masood Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai : ''main uska tujh se ziyada haq daar hun, (farishto !) merey bandey se darguzar farmaao.'' rawahu Muslim."
2793,"Hazrat Abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''khareed-farokht kartey waqt ziyada qasmen uthaney se bacho, kyonkey us se tijarat ko farogh to milta hai lekin phir wo khatam ho jati hai.'' rawahu Muslim."
2794,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''qasam sodey ko riwaaj deti hai lekin barkat khatam ho jati hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
2795,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah roze-qiyamat teen qism ke logon se kalam farmaeyga na (nazare-rehmat sey) unki taraf dekhega aur na hi unka tazkiya farmaeyga aur unke liye dardnak azab hoga.'' Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kiya, wo to nakam aur na-murad ho gaey, Allah ke Rasool ! wo kon log hain? farmaya : ''izaar latkaaney wala, ehsan jatlaaney wala aur jhooti qism se apna soda bechney wala.'' rawahu Muslim."
2796,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''sachcha amanat daar taajir Anbiya (Alaihimussalam), siddiqeen aur shuda ke sath hoga.'' rawahu Tirmizi, Darmi aur Dar-Qutni."
2797,"Hazrat ibne-Maja ne isey ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kiya hai, aur Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu ibne-Maja."
2798,"Hazrat Qais bin Abi Gharzaa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke daur mein ham (taajiron) ko ''brokar'' (dalaal) kaha jata tha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamarey paas se guzrey to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamen eik aisa naam diya jo ke us se behtar tha, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''taajiron ki jamaat ! khareed-farokht kartey waqt fizul aur bekaar baaten ho jati hain aur qasmen bhi hoti hain, lihaza tum iskey sath sadqe ko shamil kar liya karo.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood, Tirmizi, Nasai aur ibne-Maja."
2799,"Hazrat Ubaid bin Rifaa apney walid se aur wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''taajiron ko faajiron (gunahgaaron) ke khaa'ne mein jama kiya jaeyga alawa uskey jisney taqwa ikhtiyar kiya, neki ki aur sadqa kiya.'' rawahu Tirmizi, ibne-Maja aur Darmi."
2800,"Hazrat Imam Behaqi ne Bara (Raziallahu anhu) se Shobil-emaan mein riwayat kiya hai, aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees Hasan Sahih hai.  (rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan)."
2801,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' bai khiyaar ke ilawa kharid-bikri karney waley mein se her eik ko, judaa na honey se pehley tak (saudey ko pukhta karney ya katm karney ka ( ikhtiyar hai.'' Bukhari, Muslim. aur Muslim ki eik riwayat mein hai, jab do bai karney waley bai kartey hain to unhen eik doosrey se juda honey se pehley tak apney saudey ke barey mein ikhtiyar hota hai, ya phir unki bai (sauda) khiyaar ho, pas jab unki bai khiyar hogi to wo wajib ho jaeygi .'' muttafaq aleh. aur Tirmizi ki eik riwayat mein hai : ''kharid-bikri karney walon ko eik doosrey se juda honey se pehley tak ikhtiyar baqi rehta hai, ya phir unhoney bai khiyaar ki ho. aur sahihain ki riwayat mein hai : '' ya un dono mein se koi eik apney sathi se kahey ke tujhey ikhtiyar hasil hai. ( یختارا (ke bajaey ( اِختَر ( '' ikhtiyar ki shart kar '' ka lafz hai."
2802,"Hazrat Hakim bin Hizam (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' kharid-bikri karney walon ko juda honey tak ikhtiyar baqi rehta hai, agar unhoney sach bola aur) maal ke barey mein) wazahat ki to un dono ke liye unki bai mein barkat dal di jati hai aur agar unhoney (maal ke naqs waghera ko) chipaya aur jhoot bola to unki bai se barkat khatam ho jati hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
2803,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik aadmi ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se farmaya : saudey mein merey sath dhoka ho jata hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum sauda karo to kaha karo : dhoka faraib nahin chalega.'' wo aadmi ye alfaz kaha karta tha. muttafaq aleh."
2804,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib apney walid se aur wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' kharido farokht karney walon ko judaa honey se pehley tak ikhtiyar hota hai siwaey iske ke bai ikhtiyar ho, aur uskey liye is dar ke pesh nazar apney sathi se juda hona jayez nahin ke wo us ( bai ( ki wapsi ka mutalba na karey.'' rawahu Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood w Nasai."
2805,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' dono bahami (aapsi) razamandi ke baghair eik-doosrey se juda na hon.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
2806,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik eraab ko saudey ke baad ikhtiyar diya. Tirmizi, aur farmaya : ye hadees sahih gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi ."
2807,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne sood khaney waley, khilaney waley, likhney waley aur uski gawahi deney walon par lanat farmaai, aur farmaya : ''(gunah mein) wo sab barabar hain.'' rawahu Muslim."
2808,"Hazrat Ubada bin Saamit (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' soney ke badley sona , chaandi ke badley chaandi , gehun ke badley gehun , jo ke badley jo , khajoor ke badley khajoor , aur namak ke badley namak eik doosrey ke barabar hon aur naqd-b-naqd hon, jab ye asnaaf badal jaeyn to phir agar wo naqd hon to jaisey chaho becho .'' rawahu Muslim ."
2809,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''sona soney ke badley, chaandi chaandi ke badley , gehun gehun ke badley, jo jo ke badley, khajoor khajoor ke badley, aur namak namak ke badley barabar barabar aur naqd-b-naqd hon, jis shakhs ne ziyada diya ya jisney ziyada ka mutalba kya to usney soodi kaam kya, aur is mein leney wala aur deney wala barabar hain.'' rawahu Muslim ."
2810,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''soney ko soney ke barabar hi farokht karo, eik doosrey mein kami beshi na karo, chaandi ko chaandi ke barabar hi farokht karo aur eik-doosrey mein kami beshi na karo, aur is mein se ghair mojud chiz ko mojud chiz ke badley farokht na karo.'' aur eik dusri riwayat mein hai : '' soney ko soney ke badley aur chaandi ko chaandi ke badley mein baham (aapas mein) barabar wazan mein farokht karo.'' muttafaq aleh."
2811,"Hazrat Maamer bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey sun raha tha : ''anaj, anaj (ghalla ghalley) ke barabar barabar ho.'' rawahu Muslim."
2812,"Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''soney ki soney ke badley, chaandi ki chaandi ke badley, gehun ki gehun ke badley, jo ki jo ke badley aur khajoor ki khajoor ke badley udhaar bai karna sood hai lekin agar dast-badast ho to jayez hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
2813,"Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik aadmi ko khaibar par aamil muqarrar kya, to wo achi qism ki khajuren lekar aap ke paas aaya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya khaibar ki sari khajuren isi tarah ki hain?'' usney arz kya, nahin, Allah ki qism ! Allah ke Rasool! ham do saa ke badley ye eik saa aur teen saa ke badley do saa ley letey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aisey na kya karo, sari khajuren dirahmon ke hisab se bech diya karo aur phir dirahmon ke badley umda qism ki khajuren kharid liya karo.'' aur farmaya : ''wazan ki janey wali tamam chizon mein bhi yehi usool hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
2814,"Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) barni (badi umda qism ki) khajuren lekar Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne un se puchha : ''ye kahan se laye ho?'' unhoney arz kya, hamarey paas nikammi khajuren thin maine unke do saa ke iwaz unka eik saa liya hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' afsos ! afsos ! ye to bilkul sood hai, bilkul sood hai, aisey na karo, balke jab tum kharidna chaho to un khajuron ko farokht karo, phir us (qeemat) ke iwaz unhen kharido.'' muttafaq aleh."
2815,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik ghulam aaya to usney hijrat par Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki baiat ki, jabkey aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko malum na tha ke wo ghulam hai, itney mein uska Malik aaya aur uska mutalba karney laga to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey farmaya : ''usey mujhey bech do.'' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne do Habshi ghulamon ke badley mein usey kharid liya, uskey baad aap kisi se baiat nahin letey they yahan tak ke aap us se poochh letey kya wo ghulam hai ya azad?'' rawahu Muslim ."
2816,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne malum shuda wazan khajoor ke badley mein ghair malum wazan khajuron ke dher ki bai se mana farmaya hai. rawahu Muslim."
2817,"Hazrat Fazala bin abi Ubaid (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine khaibar ke din baara Dinar ke badley main eik haar kharid jis mein sona aur ghonghey they, maine us haar ko khol diya to maine is mein baara Dinar se ziyada sona paya , maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se uska tazkira kya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' usko na becha jaey yahan tak ke usey khol kar alag kar liya jaey.'' rawahu Muslim."
2818,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' logon par aisa waqt bhi aaeyga ke tamam log sood khaney waley hongey, agar koi usey nahin bhi khayega to uska asar us tak pahunch jaeyga.'' aur is tarah bhi marwi (bayan) hai ke '' uska ghubar pahunch jaeyga.'' rawahu Ahmed w Abu-Dawood w Nasai w ibne-Maja."
2819,"Hazrat Ubada bin Saamit (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' soney ko soney ke badley mein, chaandi ko chaandi, gehun ko gehun , jo ko jo , khajoor ko khajoor aur namak ko namak ke badley mein farokht na karo, haan ye ke wo barabar barabar, naqd-b-naqd aur dast badast hon. aur soney ko chaandi ke badley mein, chaandi ko soney ke badley mein , gehun ko jo ke badley mein, jo ko gehun ke badley mein, khajoor ko namak aur namak ko khajoor ke badley mein dast badast jaisey tum chaho becho.'' rawahu Shafai ."
2820,"Hazrat Saad bin abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna, aap se taza khajuron ke badley mein chhuhaarey kharidney ke barey mein sawal kya gaya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab khajoor khushk ho jati hai to kya wo ( wazan mein) kam ho jati hai? '' to us shakhs ne arz ki, ji haan , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey us se mana farmaya. rawahu Malik w Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood w Nasai w ibne-Maja ."
2821,"Hazrat Saeed bin musaiyeb (Raziallahu anhu) se mursal riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne haiwaan ke badley gosht ki bai (khareed-bikri) se mana farmaya hai. Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : ye jahiliyat ke juey ki eik surat thi. , ( rawahu al-baghwi fi Sharahus-sunnah ( ."
2822,Hazrat Samra bin Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne haiwaan ke badley haiwaan ki udhar bai (kareed-bikri) se mana farmaya. rawahu Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood w Nasai w ibne-Maja w Darmi.
2823,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen lashkar tayyar karney ka hukm farmaya to oont kam pad gaey, phir aapney unhen hukm farmaya ke wo sadqe ki jawan oontniyon ke wade par oont ley lein, chunanche wo eik oont do oontniyon ke badley sadqa ke oont aaney tak ke wada par ley rahey they. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
2824,Hazrat Usama bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''sood udhaar mein hai.'' aur eik dusri riwayat mein hai : ''jo naqad b-naqd ho is mein sood nahin.'' muttafaq aleh.
2825,"Hazrat ghaseelul-malaika Hanzala (Raziallahu anhu) ke bete Abdullah bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs jantey huey eik dirham sood khata hai to ye chhattis martaba zina karney se bhi ziyada sangeen hai.'' aur Imam Behaqi ne Shobil-emaan mein ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kya hai, aur ye izafa naqal kartey huey farmaya : ''jis shakhs ka gosht haram se tayyar hua ho to aag uski ziyada haq daar hai.'' ( rawahu Ahmed w Dar-Qutni w al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( ."
2826,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''sood ke (gunah ke) sattar hissey hain, un mein se kam tar gunah ye hai ke aadmi apni maa se nikah karey.'' ( rawahu ibne-Maja w al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( ."
2827,"Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' be-shak sood chaahey kitna bhi ziyada ho jaey lekin uska anjam faqro-zillat hai.'' un dono riwayaat ko ibne-Maja aur Behaqi ne Shobil-emaan mein jabkey aakhiri hadees ko Imam Ahmed ne riwayat kya hai. ( rawahu ibne-Maja w al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan w Ahmed)."
2828,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Mairaj ki raat main eik qom ke paas aaya jinkey pet gharon ki manind they jin mein sanp unke pet ke bahar se nazar aa rahey they, maine kaha : Jibrael ! ye kon log hain? farmaya : ''sood khor.'' rawahu Ahmed w ibne-Maja ."
2829,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko suna aapney sood khaney waley, khilaney waley, uskey likhney waley aur Zakat na deney waley par lanat farmaey, aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) nauha karney se mana kya kartey they. rawahu Nasai."
2830,"Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke aakhiri aayat sood ke barey mein nazil hui aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) faut ho gaey lekin aapney uski hamen tafseer nahin batai thi, tum sood aur misl sood tarak kar do. rawahu ibne-Maja w Darmi ."
2831,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi kisi ko qarz dey , phir wo ( maqrooz ( shakhs usko koi tohfa dey ya usey sawari par bithaaey to wo is par Sawar ho na us tohfe ko qubul karey. albatta agar unke darmiyan ye kaam (tohfon ka tabadla waghera) pehley se hi jari ho to jayez hai.'' (rawahu ibne-Maja w al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan) ."
2832,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab aadmi, aadmi ko qarz dey to phir wo hadiya qubul na karey.'' Imam Bukhari ne usey taareekh mein riwayat kya, aur al-mantaqi mein bhi isi tarah hai. ( Bukhari fi taareekha ( ."
2833,"Hazrat abu-Barda bin Abu-Musa bayan kartey hain, main Madina gaya to maine Abdullah bin Salam (Raziallahu anhu) se mulaqat ki to unhoney farmaya : tum aisey mulk mein rehtey ho jahan sood aam hai, jab tumhara kisi aadmi par koi haq ho aur wo ghaas ka eik gatha ya jo ya jangli harey chaarey ka eik gatha bator hadiya bhejey to usey na lo kyonkey wo sood hai. Bukhari ."
2834,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ''mazaabna'' se mana farmaya hai, aur wo ye hai ke wo apney baagh ka phal, agar khajoor ho to malum shuda miqdaar khushk khajoor ke sath, agar angoor ho to usey munaqqa ke sath naap kar, aur Muslim mein hai : agar kheti ho to anaj ke sath naap kar bechna, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne un sab Suraton se mana farmaya hai. Bukhari, Muslim. aur saheehain hi ki riwayat mein, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mazaabna se mana farmaya hai, aur mazaabna ye hai ke khajuron ke darkht par lagey huey phal ko khushk khajuron ke sath muqarrara pemaney se bechna, aur yun kahey ke agar ziyada ho to mera aur agar kam ho to main dunga. muttafaq aleh."
2835,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mukhahira, muhaaqla aur mazaabna se mana farmaya hai. muhaaqla ye hai ke aadmi so farq ( wazan ka pemana ( gehun ke badley kheti farokht kar dey, mazaabna ye hai ke wo so farq khajoor ke badley mein khajuron ko darakhton par farokht kar dey , aur mukhaahira ye hai ke zamin ko tihai ya chothai hissey par kaasht karney ko diya jaey. rawahu Muslim ."
2836,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne muhaaqla, mazaabna, mukhaahira, baagh ko kaee saal par thekey par deney aur istisna se mana kya hai, albatta aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne andaza laganey ki ijazat farmaey. rawahu Muslim ."
2837,"Hazrat Sehal bin abi Hashma (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne khushk khajoor ke badley taza khajoor bechney se mana farmaya, albatta aapney andaza laganey ki ijazat di, wo ye hai ke usko andaza se khushk khajuron ke iwaz bech diya jaey, taake uskey Malik taza khajuren kha saken.'' muttafaq aleh."
2838,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne paanch wasq ya us se kam khushk khajoor ke andaza se taza khajuron ko bechney ki ijazat farmaey.'' Dawud bin Husain raawi ko paanch ya paanch se kam mein shak hua . muttafaq aleh.
2839,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne phalon ki kharid-bikri se mana farmaya yahan tak ke unki salahiyat zahir ho jaey, aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne kharidney wlaey aur bechney waley dono ko mana farmaya. Bukhari, Muslim . aur Muslim ki riwayat mein hai aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne khajuron ki bai se mana farmaya yahan tak ke wo surkh ho jaeyn aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne sunbul (baaliyon) ki bai se mana farmaya yahan tak ke wo safed ho jaeyn aur aafat se bach jaeyn .'' muttafaq aleh."
2840,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne phalon ki bai se mana farmaya yahan tak ke '' زھو '' ( pukhta (ho jaeyn .'' arz kya gaya '' , زھو '' se kya murad hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' yahan tak ke wo surkh ho jaeyn, aur farmaya : ''mujhey bataao agar Allah phal rok ley to phir tum mein se koi apney musalman bhai ka maal kis chiz ke iwaz hasil kerega ?'' muttafaq aleh."
2841,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne kaee salon key saudey se mana farmaya aur aafat se honey waley nuqsan ko minhaa (kam) karney ka hukm farmaya. rawahu Muslim ."
2842,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar tum apney ( kisi musalman) bhai ko phal farokht karo aur phir is par koi aafat aa jaey to tumharey liye us se kuch lena halal nahin, tum apney bhai ka maal nahaq kis chiz ke badley hasil karogey.'' rawahu Muslim ."
2843,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, log baazar ke baalai (upri) hissey se anaj khareedtey aur usey wahin farokht kar diya kartey they, lekin Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey usi jagah par farokht karney se mana farma diya yahan tak ke wo usey muntaqil karen. Abu-Dawood. maine usey saheehain mein nahin paya. rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
2844,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs ghalla kharid ley to wo usey qabze mein leney se pehley farokht na karey.'' muttafaq aleh."
2845,aur ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ki riwayat mein hai : '' yahan tak ke wo usey naap ley.'' muttafaq aleh.
2846,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, rahi wo chiz jis se Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mana farmaya hai ke usey farokht na kya jaey yahan tak ke is par qabza kar liya jaey to wo anaj hai, aur ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : jabkey mera her chiz ke barey mein yehi khayal hai. muttafaq aleh."
2847,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''saudey ke liye tijaarati qafley ko (shehar se bahar ja kar) na milo, koi kisi key saudey par sauda na karey, mehaz qeemat badhaney ke liye boli na do, koi shahri, dehati ke liye koi maal farokht na karey, oontni aur bakri ka doodh na roko , agar koi aisa janwer kharid leta hai to doodh dohney ke baad usey dono ikhtiyar hasil hain : agar wo is par razi ho to usey rakh ley aur agar razi na ho to usey wapis kar dey aur eik saa khajoor bhi uskey sath dey.'' Bukhari, Muslim. aur Muslim ki riwayat mein hai : ''jo shakhs aisi bakri khareedey jiska doodh roka gaya ho to usey teen din tak ikhtiyar hai, agar wo usey wapis karey to uskey sath eik saa khaney ka bhi wapis karey lekin wo gehun na ho.'' muttafaq aleh."
2848,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum anaj laney walon ko raastey mein ja kar na milo, jo shakhs usey miley aur us se ghalla kharid ley, phir uska Malik baazar aa jaey to usey ikhtiyar hasil hai.'' ( chahey to soda rehney dey aur chahey to fasakh kar dey ( rawahu Muslim ."
2849,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum samane-tijarat ko shehar se bahar ja kar na milo yahan tak ke usey baazar mein utaar diya jaey.'' muttafaq aleh."
2850,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aadmi apney bhai key saudey par sauda na karey, na apney bhai ke peghame-nikah par pegham nikah bhejey magar ye ke wo usey ijazat dey dey.'' rawahu Muslim ."
2851,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aadmi apney musalman bhai key sauda tey honey tak bhaaw na karey.'' rawahu Muslim.
2852,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''koi shehri, kisi dehati ka maal farokht na karey, logon ko (apney haal par) chhod do, Allah Taala baaz ke zariey baaz ko rizq faraham karta hai.'' rawahu Muslim ."
2853,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne do tarah ke pahnaawon aur do tarah ki tijarat se mana farmaya hai. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne bai mulaamisa aur munaabiza se mana farmaya, mulaamisa ye hai ke aadmi din ya raat ke waqt kisi doosrey shakhs ke kapdey ko haath se chhuta hai aur usey ulat palat karkey nahin dekhta aur bas is tarah bai ho jati hai, jabkey munaabiza ye hai ke aadmi apna kapda doosrey shakhs ki taraf aur wo apna kapda us pehley shakhs ki taraf phainktaa hai aur bas isi tarah bin dekhey aur baghair razamandi ke sauda ho jata hai. aur do pahnaawey ye hain : un mein se eik ''Ishtimalussamma'' hai aur wo ye hai ke wo apna kapda apney kisi eik kandhey par rakhey aur uska eik pehlu zahir rahey jis par koi kapda na ho, aur doosra pehnawa ye hai ke got maar kar is tarah bethna ke us kapdey ka kuch bhi hissey uski sharm-gah par na ho. muttafaq aleh."
2854,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne kankari phenk kar sauda karney aur dhokey ka sauda karney se mana farmaya. rawahu Muslim ."
2855,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ''hablul-habla'' key saudey se mana farmaya, aur ehle jahiliyat is tarah ka sauda kiya kartey they, aur wo is tarah ke aadmi is iqrar par oontni khareedta ke ye oontni bacha janegi aur phir jab wo bacha, bacha janega tab uski qeemat ada karunga.'' muttafaq aleh."
2856,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne nar se juftii karaney par ujrat leney se mana farmaya. Bukhari ."
2857,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne oont se oontni par jufti karwaaney par ujrat leney aur kheti baadi ke liye di janey wali zamin aur pani par ujrat leney se mana farmaya. rawahu Muslim ."
2858,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne zarurat sey zyada pani farokht karney se mana farmaya. rawahu Muslim ."
2859,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''zarurat se zyada pani farokht na kya jaey taake uskey zariey ghaas farokht ki jaey.'' muttafaq aleh."
2860,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) anaj ke eik dher ke paas se guzrey to aapney apna haath is mein dakhil kya to aap ki ungliyan nam ho gaeen to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''anaj waley! ye kya hai? '' usney arz kya : Allah ke Rasool ! is par barish ho gaee thi, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum ne usey anaj ke ooper kyon na kya taake log jaan letey , ( jaan lo ( jis shakhs ne dhoka diya wo mujh se nahin .'' rawahu Muslim ."
2861,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne (ghair moayan cheezon mein) istisna karney se mana farmaya, albatta agar wo (mustashna chiz) malum ho to jayez hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
2862,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne angooron ki bai se mana farmaya yahan tak ke wo (pak kar) siyah ho jaeyn aur daanon (ghalla anaj waghera) ki bai se mana farmaya yahan tak ke wo (pak kar) sakht ho jaeyn.'' Imam Tirmizi aur Abu-Dawood ne usey isi tarah riwayat kya hai, un dono ke yahan (Anas (Raziallahu anhu)) se marwi (bayan) riwayat mein ye alfaz nahin hain : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne khajuron ki bai se mana farmaya : yahan tak ke wo surkh ho jaeyn. albatta ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) riwayat mein ye alfaz hain : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne khajuron ki bai se mana farmaya yahan tak ke wo surkh ho jaeyn. aur ye izafa jo masaabeh mein hai wo ye alfaz hain ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne khajuron ki bai se mana farmaya yahan tak ke wo surkh ho jaeyn. albatta un dono ki ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) riwayat mein mazkura alfaz mojud hain : ''aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne khajuron ki bai se mana farmaya yahan tak ke wo surkh ho jaeyn .''aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. sanda rawahu Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood."
2863,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne qarz ke sath qarz ki bai ko mamnoo qarar diya hai. rawahu Dar-Qutni .
2864,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib apney walid se aur wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne baiyana lekar bai karney se mana farmaya. rawahu Malik w Abu-Dawood w ibne-Maja ."
2865,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne majbur be bas shakhs ki bai sey, dhokey ki bai se aur phalon ki bai se is se pehley ke wo paak jaeyn mana farmaya hai. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
2866,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain kilaab qabiley ke eik aadmi ne nar se jufti karaney ki ujrat ke barey mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se masla puchha to aapney usey mana kya, to usney arz kya : Allah ke Rasool! ham to jufti karatey hain lekin (bin maangey) hadiya ke taur par hamen nawaza jata hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey hadiyatan rakhney ki ijazat de-di. rawahu Tirmizi."
2867,"Hazrat Hakim bin Hizam (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne aisi chiz bechney se mujhey mana farmaya jo merey paas mojud na ho. Tirmizi. Tirmizi ki eik dusri riwayat aur Abu-Dawood aur Nasai ki eik riwayat mein hai, wo bayan kartey hain, maine arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! koi aadmi merey paas aata hai aur mujh se koi chiz khareedna chahta hai, lekin wo merey paas nahin hoti to main usey baazar se kharid deta hun, (to kya ye jayez hai? (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo chiz terey paas na ho usey na bech.'' rawahu Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood w Nasai ."
2868,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik saudey mein do saudon se mana farmaya. rawahu Malik w Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood w Nasai ."
2869,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib apney walid se aur wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik hi martaba do saudon se mana farmaya. ( rawahu al-baghwi fi Sharahus-sunnah ( ."
2870,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib apney walid se aur wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''qarz aur sauda (eik sath) jayez nahi hai, na eik saudey mein do shartein, aur na hi us chiz ka munaafaa jayez hai jiska zaamin nahin aur us chiz ki bai bhi jayez nahin jo terey paas nahin.'' Tirmizi, Abu-Dawud, Nasai . aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees sahih hai. rawahu Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood w Nasai."
2871,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main maqam naqee par oonton ko dinaaron ke badley becha karta tha aur unki jagah dirham wasul karta tha, aur kabhi dirahmon mein bechta aur unki jagah Dinar wasul karta tha, main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to maine aap se uska tazkira kya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar tum usi roz ki qeemat wasul karo, aur jab tum dono juda ho to tumharey darmiyan lein dein baqi na ho to is mein koi harj nahin .'' rawahu Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood w Nasai w Darmi ."
2872,"Hazrat Adda bin Khalid bin hauza (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhoney eik tehreer nikali, (jiski ibarat yun thi ( ye tehreer us chiz se mutalliq hai jo Adda bin Khalid bin hauza ne Allah ke Rasool , Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se ghulam ya londi khareedi, is mein koi bimari hai na usey koi buri aadat hai aur na koi akhlaqi burai, aur ye musalman ki musalman se bai hai.'' Tirmizi. aur farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
2873,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik kambal aur piyala bechney ka irada kya to farmaya : '' us kambal aur piyaley ko kon khareedta hai?'' eik aadmi ne arz kya, main un dono ko eik dirham mein khareedta hun, to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''eik dirham se ziyada kon deta hai? '' chunanche eik aadmi ne do dirham ke iwaz unhen aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se kharid liya . rawahu Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood w ibne-Maja ."
2874,"Hazrat Waasila bin Isqaa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''jo shakhs koi aeb w naqs wali chiz bechta hai aur uskey mutalliq batata nahin to wo Allah ki narazi mein rehta hai ya farishtey is par lanat bhejtey rehtey hain.'' rawahu ibne-Maja."
2875,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs taabeer (pewand) ke baad khajoor ka darkht khareedey to agar kharidar shart qaaim na karey to uska phal bechney waley ka hai, aur jo shakhs koi ghulam bechey aur uska kuch maal ho to wo maal bechney waley ka hai, siway iskey ke kharidar uski shart qaaim kar ley.'' Muslim, aur Imam Bukhari (Raziallahu anhu) ne sirf pehla hissey hi bayan kya hai."
2876,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke wo eik zaati oont par safar kar rahey they jo ke thak chuka tha, usi beech mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uskey paas se guzrey to aapney usey maara to wo yun chalney laga ke wo pehley kabhi aisey nahin chalta tha, phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usey eik auqiya ke badley mein mujhey bech do.'' Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya, maine usey bech diya albatta maine apney ehel w ayaal tak pahunchney ki mohlat le-li, jab main Madina pahuncha to main oont lekar aap ki khidmat mein hazir hua to aapney uski qeemat mujhey ada kar di. aur eik dusri riwayat mein hai : main hazir hua to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uski qeemat bhi ada kar di aur wo oont bhi wapis kar diya. Bukhari , Muslim . aur sahih Bukhari ki dusri riwayat mein hai : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ko farmaya : ''usey qeemat ada kar do aur ziyada bhi do .'' unhoney mujhey qeemat bhi ada ki aur eik Qiraat mazeed ata kya. muttafaq aleh."
2877,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Barira (Raziallahu anhu) aain to unhoney kaha : maine no auqiya par) azadi hasil karney ke liye ( kitaabat ki hai. aur her saal eik auqiya dena hai, lihaza aap (Raziallahu anhu) meri madad farmaeyn, Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya : agar tumharey Malik pasand karen to main ye raqam eik hi martaba ada kar deti hun, aur tumhen azad kara deti hun, lekin tumhari wla ( virasat ( meri hogi , wo apney malikon ke paas gaeen to unhoney inkar kar diya aur kaha ke wla unke liye hogi , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usey kharid kar azad kar do.'' phir aap logon se khitab karney ke liye khadey huye, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Allah Taala ki hamd w sana bayan ki phir farmaya : ''logon ko kya hua ke wo aisi shartein lagatey hain jo Allah ki kitab mein nahin hain, aur jo shart Allah ki kitab mein na ho, chahey wo so shartein hon, to wo batil hain, Allah ki qaza ziyada haq rakhti hai, aur Allah ki shart ziyada moatabar hai, aur wla azad karney waley ka haq hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
2878,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne wla ko farokht karney aur usey hiba karney se mana farmaya hai. muttafaq aleh."
2879,"Hazrat Mukhlid bin khufaf bayan kartey hain, maine eik ghulam kharid to maine us se aamdani hasil ki, phir mujhey uskey eik naqs ka pata chala to main uska muqadma umr bin Abdul-Azeez (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas ley gaya to unhoney usey wapis karney ka faisla merey haq mein kya aur us se hasil honey wali aamdani wapis lotaney ka faisla merey khilaf kya, main Urwa (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas gaya, aur unhen sara waqia bayan kya to unhoney farmaya : main pichley pahar unke paas jaaunga aur unhen bataaunga ke Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne mujhey bataya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne is tarah ke mamley ka faisla kya ke khiraaj, zamanat ke badley mein hai, Urwa (Raziallahu anhu) pichley pahar unke paas gaey (aur unhen bataya ( to unhoney merey haq mein faisla kya ke main us shakhs se wo khiraaj ki raqam wapis ley lun jo unhoney mujh se lekar usey dilwai thi. (rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah ( ."
2880,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab kharido-farokht karney walon ke darmiyan ikhtilaf ho jaey to bechney waley ki baat moatabar hogi, jabkey kharidar ko ikhtiyar hasil hoga. Tirmizi, ibne-Maja aur Darmi ki riwayat mein hai. farmaya : ''jab kharido farokht karney walon ke darmiyan ikhtilaf ho jaey jabkey farokht shuda chiz wesay hi mojud ho aur un dono ke paas koi sabut na ho to bechney waley ki baat moatabar hogi , ya phir wo bai wapis kar dengey.'' rawahu Tirmizi w ibne-Maja w Darmi ."
2881,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs kisi musalman ka sauda wapis kar dey to roze-qiyamat Allah Taala uski khataaein maaf farma dega.'' Abu-Dawud, ibne-Maja . jabkey Sharahus-sunnah mein masaabeh ke alfaz ke sath Shureh Shami (Raziallahu anhu) se mursal riwayat hai, ( rawahu Abu-Dawood w ibne-Maja w fi Sharahus-sunnah ( ."
2882,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' pehley zamaney main eik aadmi ne doosrey aadmi se zamin khareedi to jis shakhs ne zamin khareedi thi usney zamin main eik ghada paya jis mein sona tha, jis shakhs ne zamin khareedi thi usney usey kaha : tum apna sona mujh se le-lo kyonkey maine to tum se sirf zamin khareedi thi, sona nahin kharid tha. zamin bechney waley ne kaha : maine zamin aur jo kuch is mein hai sab tumhen bech diya tha, wo dono apna muqadma eik aadmi ke paas ley gaey, to jis aadmi ke paas wo muqadma lekar gaey they, usney kaha : kya tumhari aulad hai? un mein se eik ne kaha : mera eik ladka hai aur doosrey ne kaha : meri eik ladki hai, to us aadmi ne kaha : ladkey ki ladki se shaadi kar do , aur us ( maal ( ko un dono par kharch kar do aur is mein se kuch sadqa kar do .'' muttafaq aleh."
2883,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Madina tashrif laye to wo log phalon ke barey mein, saal, do saal aur teen saal ke liye bai-slam kya kartey they, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs kisi chiz mein bai-slam karey to wo tey shuda naap w wazan aur tey shuda muddat ke liye bai-slam (kisi chiz ki peshgi raqm de-kar) karey."
2884,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik Yahudi se eik muddat ke liye ghalla liya aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apni lohey ki zireh uskey paas girwi rakhi. muttafaq aleh."
2885,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne wafat pai to aap ki zireh tees saa jo ke iwaz eik Yahudi ke paas girwi thi. Bukhari."
2886,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab sawari ka janwer girwi ho to b-qadr kharch is par sawari ki ja sakti hai aur agar doodh wala janwer girwi ho to b-qadr kharch uska doodh piya ja sakta hai, aur jo shakhs sawari karta hai aur doodh peeta hai, usi ke zimme kharcha hai.'' Bukhari ."
2887,"Hazrat Saad bin Musaiyeb (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''rehan, marhoona chiz ko uskey Malik sey, jisney usey rehan rakha hai, nahin rok sakta, uska faeyda bhi usi (malik) ko hoga aur uska nuqsan bhi usi ko hoga.'' Imam Shafai (Raziallahu anhu) ne usey mursal riwayat kya hai. rawahu Shafai."
2888,"Hazrat us riwayat ki misl ya uskey maana ke misl jo uskey mukhalif nahin, Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se muttasil riwayat bhi hai. rawahu ibne-Maja ."
2889,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''naap ehle-Madina ka moatabar hai jabkey wazan ehle-Makka ka moatabar hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood w Nasai.
2890,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne naap tol walon ko farmaya : ''bila-shuba do kaam tumharey zimme aisey lagaey gaey hain, jin (mein kami beshi) ki wajeh se tum se pehli qomen halakat ka shikar huin.'' rawahu Tirmizi ."
2891,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs kisi chiz ke barey mein bai-slam karey to wo is par qabza karney se pehley usey kisi aur ko na dey.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood w ibne-Maja."
2892,"Hazrat Maamer (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs zakhira andozi karta hai wo gunahgaar hai.'' aur ham umr (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hadees : ''banu Nazeer ke amwaal'' ko insha Allah Taala (Fai key baab) mein zikr karengey. (rawahu Muslim)."
2893,"Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' ( baazar mein) ghalla laney walon ko rizq diya jata hai, jabkey zakhira andoz mal-oon hai.'' rawahu ibne-Maja w Darmi ."
2894,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke zamaney mein qiimatein chadh gaeen to Sahaba ne arz kya, Allah ke Rasool! aap hamarey liye qiimtein muqarrar farma den, to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''be-shak Allah hi qiimtein muqarrar karney wala hai, wohi tangi w kushadgi ka Malik aur rizq deney wala hai, aur main ummid karta hun ke main is haal mein apney rab se mulaqat karun ke tum mein se koi khoon aur maal ke mutalliq mujh se mutalba na karta ho.'' rawahu Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood w ibne-Maja."
2895,"Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''jo shakhs musalmanon par ghalla rok dey (zakhira andozii karey) to Allah is par juzaam ka marz aur iflas musallat kar deta hai.'' ibne-Maja, Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan, aur rizeen ne usey apni kitab mein riwayat kya hai. rawahu ibne-Maja, Baihaqi w rizeen."
2896,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs qeemat badhaney ke liye chaalis roz tak zakhira andozi karta hai to wo Allah se la-talluq hua, aur Allah Taala us-se la-talluq hua.'' rawahu rizeen ."
2897,"Hazrat Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''zakhira andoz shakhs bahut bura hai, agar Allah qiimtein kam kar deta hai to wo ghamgin ho jata hai, aur agar wo unhen badha deta hai to khush ho jata hai.'' Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan, aur rizeen ne usey apni kitab mein bayan kya hai. rawahu al-Behaqi w rizeen."
2898,Hazrat abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs chaalis roz tak ghalla zakhira karey aur phir wo usey sadqa bhi kar dey to wo uska kaffara nahin ho sakta. '' rawahu rizeen .
2899,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs muflis ho jaey aur koi aadmi apna maal bilkul usi surat mein pa ley to ye (maal wala) shakhs dusron ki nisbat us maal ka ziyada haq daar hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
2900,"Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke daur main eik aadmi ko phalon ki tijarat mein khasara hua to uska qarz bahut ziyada ho gaya, us surat mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''us par sadqa karo.'' logon ne is par sadqa kya lekin wo uskey qarz ki adaegi ke barabar na hua, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uskey qarz khuwahon se farmaya : ''jo milta hai ley lo, tumharey liye bas yehi kuch hai.'' rawahu Muslim."
2901,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''eik aadmi qarz diya karta tha, wo apney mulaazim se kaha karta tha : jab tum kisi tangdast ke paas jaao to usko ( qarz ( maaf kar diya karo, shayad ke Allah hamen maaf farma dey. farmaya : usney Allah se mulaqat ki to usney usey maaf farma diya.'' muttafaq aleh."
2902,"Hazrat abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ko ye pasand ho ke Allah usey roze-qiyamat ki takleefon se najat dey dey to wo tangdast ko mohlat dey ya usey ( qarz ( maaf kar dey .'' rawahu Muslim ."
2903,"Hazrat abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''jo shakhs kisi tangdast ko mohlat dey ya usey qarz maaf kar dey to Allah usey roze-qiyamat ki takleefon se najat dey dega.'' rawahu Muslim ."
2904,"Hazrat abu-Yusr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : jo shakhs kisi tangdast ko mohlat dey ya usey qarz maaf kar dey to Allah usey apney (arsh ke) saye mein saya ata farmaeyga.'' rawahu Muslim ."
2905,"Hazrat abu-Raafe (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik no umr oont qarz liya, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas sadqa ke oont aaye to abu-Raafe (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, aapney mujhey hukm farmaya ke main us aadmi ko uskey no umr oont ka qarz utaar dun, maine arz kya : tamam oont behtareen qism ke saat saal ki umr ke hain, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usey yehi dey do, kyonkey behtareen shakhs wo hai jo qarz ada karney mein achcha ho.'' rawahu Muslim ."
2906,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se qarz ki wapsi ka taqaza kya to usney aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par sakhti ki to aap ke Sahaba ne usey maarney ka irada kya, to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usey chhod do, kyonkey sahibe-haq (qarz khuwah) baaten karney ka haq rakhta hai, tum eik oont kharid kar usey dey do.'' Sahaba ne arz kya is se badi umr ka oont milta hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usey hi kharid kar usey dey do, kyonkey tum mein se behtareen wo hai jo tum mein se qarz ada karney mein behtar hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
2907,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''maal daar shakhs ka (qarz ki adaegi mein) taal matol karna zulm hai, agar tum mein se kisi ko kisi maal daar shakhs (yani zaamin) ke peechey laga diya jaey (ke us se qarz wasul kar lo) to lag jana chahiye.'' muttafaq aleh."
2908,"Hazrat Kab bin Malik se riwayat hai ke unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke daur mein ibne-abi Hadrad (Raziallahu anhu) se masjid mein apney qarz ka mutalba kya to un dono ki aawazen buland ho gaeen yahan tak ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen apney ghar mein sun liya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) un dono ki taraf aaye yahan tak ke aapney apney hujrey ka parda utha kar Kab bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ko aawaz di, farmaya : ''Kaab!'' unhoney arz kya, Allah ke Rasool! hazir hun, aapney apney haath se ishara kya ke uska aadha qarz maaf kar do. Kab (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya : Allah ke Rasool! maine kar diya, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne (ibne-abi hadrad (Raziallahu anhu) sey) farmaya : ''khada ho aur uska qarz ada kar .'' muttafaq aleh."
2909,"Hazrat Salma bin Akwa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas bethey huey they ke eik janaza laya gaya, Sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya : uski Namaz janaza padhaein, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya is par koi qarz hai? '' unhoney arz kya : nahin. to aapney uski Namaz janaza padhaai, phir aap ke paas eik aur janaza laya gaya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya is par koi qarz hai? '' arz kya gaya : ji haan, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya usney koi chiz tarka chhodi hai? '' unhoney arz kya : teen deenar, aapney uski Namaz janaza padhi, phir teesra janaza laya gaya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya is par koi qarz hai?'' unhoney arz kya : teen deenar, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya usney koi tarka chhoda hai? '' unhoney arz kya : nahin, farmaya : ''apney sathi ki Namaz janaza padho .'' abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya : Allah ke Rasool ! aap uski Namaz janaza padhein aur uska qarz merey zimma raha ( mein ada karunga ( tab aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uski Namaz janaza padhaai . Bukhari ."
2910,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs bator qarz logon ka maal hasil karta hai aur wo usey ada karna chahta hai to Allah Taala usey ada karney ki tofiq se nawazta hai, aur jo shakhs usey talaf karney ke liye hasil karta hai to Allah Taala usey talaf farma dega.'' Bukhari ."
2911,"Hazrat abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik aadmi ne arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! mujhey bataeyn agar main Sabit qadmi sey, sawab ki ummid se Allah ki raah mein dushman ka muqabla kartey huey Shaheed ho jaaun to kya Allah merey gunah maaf farma dega? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''haan.'' jab wo wapis chala gaya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey aawaz di, farmaya : '' haan, albatta qarz maaf nahin hoga, Jibrael (Alaihissalam) ne isi tarah kaha hai.'' rawahu Muslim ."
2912,Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' qarz ke siwa Shaheed ke tamam gunah maaf kar diye jatey hain.'' rawahu Muslim .
2913,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, kisi maqrooz ka janaza, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas laya jata to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmatey : ''kya usney apney qarz ki adaegi ke liye kuch chhoda hai? ''agar aap ko bataya jata ke usney jo kuch chhoda hai us se qarz ada ho jaeyga to aap Namaz janaza padhatey , warna (na padhatey) musalmanon se kehtey : ''apney sathi ki Namaz janaza padho .'' jab Allah Taala ne aap ko futoohaat nasib farmaain to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne khitab kartey huey farmaya : ''main mominon ka unki jinnon se bhi ziyada haq daar hun, jo momin faut ho jaey aur wo maqrooz ho to uska qarz merey zimme hai, aur jo shakhs maal chhod jaey to wo uskey warison ke liye hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
2914,"Hazrat Abu-Khalda zarqi bayan kartey hain, ham apney eik sathi , jo ke muflis ho gaya tha, ke barey mein Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaye to unhoney farmaya : ye is tarah ka maamla hai jiskey barey mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne faisla kya : ''jo shakhs faut ho jaey ya muflis ho jaey to maal ka Malik us maal ka ziyada haq daar hai jabkey wo us maal ko bilkul usi haalat mein paey .'' rawahu Shafai w ibne-Maja ."
2915,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' momin ki rooh apney qarz ki wajeh se muallaq rehti hai yahan tak ke wo ( qarz ( uski taraf se ada kar diya jaey.'' rawahu Shafai w Ahmed w Tirmizi w ibne-Maja w Darmi ."
2916,"Hazrat Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' maqrooz shakhs apney qarz ki wajeh se mahboos hai, wo roze-qiyamat apney rab se tanhai ki shikayat kerega.'' ( rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah ( ."
2917,"bayan kiya gaya hai ke Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) qarz liya kartey they, unke qarz chahey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaye (aur qarz ka mutalba kya) to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unke qarz ki adaeygi mein unka sara maal farokht kar diya yahan tak ke Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas koi chiz baqi na rahi. riwayat mursal hai. ye alfaz masaabeh ke hain. maine Muntaqa ke siwa usey usool ki kitabon mein nahin paya ."
2918,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Kab bin Malik bayan kartey hain, Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) badey sabir aur sakhi insan they, wo koi chiz paas nahin rakhtey they aur hamesha maqrooz rehtey they yahan tak ke unka sara maal qarz ki adaegi mein jata raha, wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur aap se arz kya ke aap uskey qarz khuwahon se sifarish karen, agar wo (qarzkhuwah) kisi ko chhodtey to wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khatir Muaz ko chhodtey, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne un (qarz khuwahon) ki khatir Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ka sara maal bech diya, yahan tak ke Muaz ke paas koi chiz na bachi . sunan Saeed bin Mansoor , ye riwayat mursal hai."
2919,"Hazrat shareed (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' ( qarz ki adaegi mein) taal matol karney waley maal daar shakhs ki be Izzati karna aur usey saza dena jayez hai.'' ibne-Mubarak (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : uski be Izzati karney se ye murad hai ke us se sakht kalaami karna jayez hai, aur usko saza deney se murad hai ke usey qaid karna jayez hai. rawahu Abu-Dawood w Nasai ."
2920,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas eik janaza laya gaya taake aap uski Namaz janaza padhein, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tumharey sathi par qarz hai? '' unhoney arz kya : ji haan, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne puchha : ''kya usney uski adaegi ke liye koi maal chhoda hai?'' unhoney arz kya : nahin, farmaya : ''tum apney sathi ki Namaz janaza padho.'' Ali bin abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya, Allah ke Rasool! uska qarz merey zimmey raha, to phir aap aagey badhey aur uski Namaz janaza padhi , aur eik dusri riwayat mein usi ka ham-maani mafhoom riwayat kya gaya hai, aur farmaya : ''Allah ne tumhari gardan ko aag se azad kar diya jaisey tum ne apney musalman bhai ki gardan ko azad kara diya. jo koi musalman banda apney bhai ki taraf se uska qarz ada karta hai to roze-qiyamat Allah uski gardan ko) aag sey) azad farmaeyga .'' (rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah) ."
2921,"Hazrat Soban (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs is haal mein faut ho ke wo kibr w khayanat aur qarz se bari ho to wo jannat mein dakhil hoga.'' rawahu Tirmizi w ibne-Maja w Darmi."
2922,"Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kabeera gunahon ke baad, Allah ke yahan sab se bada gunah jis se Allah ne mana farmaya hai wo ye hai ke banda marney ke baad apney rab se us haal mein mulaqat karey ke uskey zimme qarz ho aur wo uski adaegi ke liye koi chiz na chodey.'' rawahu Ahmed w Abu-Dawood ."
2923,"Hazrat Amr bin Auf Muzni (Raziallahu anhu), Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' musalmanon ke darmiyan suleh jayez hai, aisi suleh ke siwa jo kisi halal ko haram kar dey ya kisi haram ko halal kar dey, aur is shart ke siwa jo halal ko haram kar dey ya haram ko halal kar dey, musalman apni sharton par Sabit hain.'' Tirmizi, ibne-Maja, Abu-Dawood aur unki riwayat ( عَلیٰ شُرُوْطِھِمْ ( tak hai. rawahu Tirmizi w ibne-Maja ."
2924,"Hazrat Suwed bin Qais (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main aur Makhrifa abdi tijarat ke liye hijr se kapda lekar Makka aaye to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) pedal chaltey huey hamarey paas tashrif laye aur aapney eik shalwaar ke kapdey ki ham se qeemat tey ki to ham ne aap ko farokht kar diya, wahan eik aadmi tha jo ujrat par wazan kya karta tha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey farmaya : ''wazan kar aur jhukta wazan kar.'' (yani purey se kuch ziyada). Ahmed, Abu-Dawud, Tirmizi, ibne-Maja, Darmi. aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. rawahu Ahmed w Abu-Dawood w Tirmizi w ibne-Maja w Darmi ."
2925,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, mera Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par kuch qarz tha, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne wo mujhey ada kya aur mujhey mazeed ata kya. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
2926,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Ubai Rabeea (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujh se chaalis hazar dirham qarz liya, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas maal aaya to aapney wo mujhey wapis kar diya, aur farmaya : ''Allah taala tumharey ehel w maal mein barkat farmaey, qarz ki jaza hi shukriya ada karna aur qarz ada karna hai.'' rawahu Nasai."
2927,"Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' kisi ka kisi shakhs par koi haq ho, aur wo ( haq leney wala ( usey mohlat dey to her roz ke badley usey sadqa ka sawab milega. rawahu Ahmed ."
2928,"Hazrat Saad bin Atwal (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, mera bhai faut ho gaya aur usney teen so Dinar aur chhotey chhotey bachey chhodey , maine irada kya ke main ( ye raqam ( un par kharch karun, lekin Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey farmaya : '' tera bhai apney qarz ki wajeh se mahboos hai, ( pehley ( uski taraf se qarz ada karo.'' wo bayan kartey hain. main gaya aur uski taraf se qarz ada kya, phir main wapis aaya to arz kya, Allah ke Rasool! maine uski taraf se sara qarz ada kar diya hai, sirf eik aurat baqi reh gaee hai jo do Dinar ka mutalba karti hai. jabkey uskey paas koi daleel nahin, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usey dey do kyonkey wo sachi hai.'' rawahu Ahmed ."
2929,"Hazrat Muhammad bin Abdullah bin Jahash (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham masjid ke sehan mein bethey huey they, jahan janaazey rakhey jatey they, jabkey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamarey darmiyan bethey huey they, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne aasman ki taraf nazar utha kar dekha phir nazar ko jhukaya aur apna haath apni peshani par rakh kar) tajjub sey) farmaya : '' Subhanallah ! Subhanallah ! kaisi sakhti nazil hui .'' raawi bayan kartey hain, ham din bhar aur puri raat khamosh rahey, aur ham ne khair hi khair dekhi , yahan tak ke subh ho gaee , Muhammad ( raawi ( bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se sawal kya, wo kon sa azab hai jo nazil hua ? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' qarz ke barey mein, us zaat ki qism jiskey haath mein Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki jaan hai! agar koi aadmi Allah ki raah mein Shahid kar diya jaey, wo phir zinda ho, phir Allah ki raah mein Shaheed kar diya jaey, phir zinda ho, phir Allah ki raah mein Shaheed kar diya jaey, phir zinda ho aur uskey zimmey qarz ho to wo jannat mein nahin jaeyga, yahan tak ke uska qarz ada kar diya jaey.'' Ahmed . aur Sharahus-sunnah mein uski misl hai. ( rawahu Ahmed w fi Sharahus-sunnah ( ."
2930,"Hazrat zohra bin mabad se riwayat hai ke unke dada Abdullah bin Hisham (Raziallahu anhu) unhen baazar ley jatey aur ghalla khareedtey, phir ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) aur ibne-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) unhen miltey to wo unhen (Abdullah bin Hisham (Raziallahu anhu) sey) kehtey : hamen bhi shareek kar lo , kyonkey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne aap ke liye barkat ki dua farmaai hai, wo unhen shareek kar letey, kabhi-kabhi unhen purey oont ke saman ka nafa ho jata to wo usey apney ghar ki taraf bhej detey, aur Abdullah bin Hisham (Raziallahu anhu) ko unki walida Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas lekar gaee thin to aapney uskey sar par piyaar se haath phera , aur uskey liye barkat ki dua ki thi."
2931,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ansaar ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se arz kya, aap hamarey aur hamarey (Muhajir) bhaiyon ke darmiyan khajuron ke darkht taqseem farma den, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' nahin, ( unhoney muhajrin se kaha ( tum mehnat karo, ham tumhen pedawar mein shareek kar lengey . unhon ( muhajrin ( ne kaha : ham ne sun liya aur ham ne maan liya . Bukhari ."
2932,"Hazrat Urwa bin abi jaad al-Barqi (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen eik Dinar diya taake wo aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke liye eik bakri khareedey. usney aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke liye do bakriyan khareedein, aur phir un mein se eik bakri eik Dinar mein farokht kar di, aur eik bakri aur eik Dinar aap ki khidmat mein pesh kar diya, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uski bai mein barkat ki dua farmaey, pas agar wo mitti bhi kharid letey to is mein nafa kamatey they. Bukhari."
2933,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) marfoo riwayat bayan kartey hain ke Allah azz-w-jall farmata hai : ''jab do sharaakat daaron mein se koi eik apney sathi se khayanat nahin karta to main unka teesra hota hun, jab wo us se khayanat karta hai to main un dono mein se nikal jata hun.'' Abu-Dawood. aur rizeen ne ye izafa naqal kya hai : '' aur shetan aa jata hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood w rizeen ."
2934,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs tumharey paas amanat rakhey to tum amanat wapis kar do, aur jo shakhs tum se khayanat karey to tum us se khayanat na karo.'' rawahu Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood w Darmi ."
2935,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine khaibar janey ka irada kya to maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar salam kya aur arz kya main khaibar janey ka irada rakhta hun, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum merey wakeel ke paas jaao to us se pandarah wasq khajuren ley lena , aur agar wo tujh se koi nishani talab karey to apna haath uskey halaq par rakh dena .'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
2936,"Hazrat Suheb (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''teen chizon mein barkat hai, eik muddat tak ( udhaar ( sauda karna, Muzaribat karna, aur gehun mein jo milaana ghar mein istimal ke liye, tijarat ke liye nahin.'' rawahu ibne-Maja ."
2937,"Hazrat Hakim bin Hizam (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey eik Dinar de-kar bheja taake wo us se aap ke liye qurbani khareedey, usney eik Dinar ka mendha kharid aur do Dinar mein bech diya, wo phir wapis gaya aur eik Dinar ki qurbani khareedi, aur wo qurbani ka janwer aur wo Dinar jo manaafa hua tha lekar hazir hua , to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne wo Dinar sadqa kar diya aur uskey liye dua farmaai, ke uski tijarat mein barkat dal di jaey. rawahu Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood ."
2938,"Hazrat Saeed bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs zulm se baalisht barabar zamin hasil karta hai to roze-qiyamat saat zaminon ka toq uskey galey mein dala jaeyga.'' muttafaq aleh."
2939,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' koi shakhs kisi aadmi ki ijazat ke baghair uskey janwer ka doodh na dohey, kya tum mein se koi shakhs pasand karta hai ke uskey kamrey mein ja kar godaam ka tala tod diya jaey aur uska anaj waghera nikal liya jaey, isi tarah unke janweron ke than unke khaney ko jama w mehfooz rakhtey hain.'' rawahu Muslim ."
2940,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apni kisi zauja mohtarma ke paas they to aap ki kisi zauja mohtarma ne plate mein khana bheja to jinkey ghar Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tashrif farma they unhoney khaadim ke haath par maara to wo plate gir kar toot gaee, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne plate ke tukdey ikhattey kiye, aur bikhrey huey khaney ko uthaya, sath mein kehney lagey : ''tumhari maa ne ghairat khai.'' phir aapney khaadim ko roka yahan tak ke usey zauja mohtarma ke ghar sey, jinkey ghar aap tashrif farma they, sahih plate di aur wo tuti hui plate us zauja mohtarma ke ghar rakh di jinhon ne todii thi. Bukhari ."
2941,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Yazid (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne daaka dalney aur musla karney (maiyat ke aaza kaatney) se mana farmaya. Bukhari ."
2942,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke daur mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke bete Ibrahim ki wafat ke din Suraj girahan hua to aapney chhe ruku'on aur chaar sajdon se Sahaba ko) do rakaat ( Namaz padhaai, aap Namaz se farigh huey to Suraj apni asli ( chamak daar ( haalat par aa chuka tha, aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis jis chiz ka tum se wada kya gaya maine apni is Namaz mein usey dekh liya, jahannam merey samney laee gaee aur ye us waqt thi jab tum ne mujhey dekha ke main, is andeshey ke peshe-nazar ke kahin uski haraarat mujhey apni lapet mein na le-ley, peechey hat gaya, yahan tak ke maine khondi waley shakhs ko aag main apni antadiyaan ghaseet-tey huey dekha, wo apni khondi se hajiyon ki chizen charaaya karta tha agar pata chal jata to kehta : ye chizen khondi se latak gaeen thin, aur agar pata na chalta to wo usey ley jata, aur yahan tak ke maine is mein billi wali khatoon bhi dekhi jisney usey baandh rakha tha, wo usey khud khilati na usey chhod deti ke wo zamin ke keedey makodey kha leti, yahan tak ke wo bhook se mar gaee, phir jannat pesh ki gaee , aur ye us waqt tha jab tum ne mujhey aagey badhtey huey dekha, yahan tak ke main apni jagah par khada ho gaya aur maine apna haath badhaya aur main uska phal lena chahta tha ke tum usey dekh lo, lekin phir mujhey zahir hua ke main ( aisey ( na karun .'' rawahu Muslim ."
2943,"Hazrat Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ko bayan kartey huey suna : Madina mein) dushman ki aamad ka ( shor sa utha to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) se mandoob naami ghoda mustaar liya aur is par Sawar ho gaey, jab aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) wapis tashrif laye to farmaya : '' ham ne koi chiz nahin dekhi, albatta ham ne ( tez raftari mein) usey samandar paya .'' muttafaq aleh."
2944,Hazrat Saeed bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs banjar zamin ko abad karey to wo usi ki hai jabkey rag zalim ka koi haq nahin .'' ( ghair ki zamin mein kaashtkaari ka koi haq nahin) rawahu Ahmed w Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood .
2945,"Hazrat Imam Malik ne Urwa se mursal riwayat kya hai, aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. rawahu Malik."
2946,"Hazrat Abu-Harra Raqashi apney chacha se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''sun lo! zulm na karo, kisi musalman ka maal uski khushi ke baghair halal nahin.'' ( rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan w Daar-qutni) ."
2947,"Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Islam mein Jalab, Janab aur shighaar nahin aur jo shakhs koi lot maar karey to wo ham mein se nahin .'' rawahu Tirmizi ."
2948,"Hazrat Saaib bin Yazid apney walid se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se koi shakhs apney bhai ki lathi hansi mazaq ke taur par usey ghussa dilaney ke liye na ley , jo shakhs apney bhai ki lathi le-ley to wo usey wapis kar dey .'' Tirmizi, Abu-Dawud, aur Abu-Dawood ki riwayat ( جَادًّا ( tak hai. rawahu Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood ."
2949,"Hazrat Samra (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs apna churaya hua maal bilkul usi haalat mein kisi shakhs ke paas paey to wo shakhs us (ko hasil karney (ka ziyada haq daar hai, aur kharidar us bechney waley ka peecha kerega.'' rawahu Ahmed w Abu-Dawood w Nasai ."
2950,"Hazrat Samra (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' haath par wajib hai ke usney jo liya hai wo wapis karey.'' rawahu Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood w ibne-Maja ."
2951,"Hazrat Haram bin Saad Muhayyesa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) ki oontni eik baagh mein dakhil ho gaee to usney wahan nuqsan kiya, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne faisla kartey huey farmaya : ''baaghbaanon ki zimme-daari hai ke wo din ke waqt unki hifazat karen, albatta jo janwer raat ke waqt nuqsan kar den to phir us (nuqsan) ke zimmedar uskey Malik hain.'' rawahu Malik, Abu-Dawood aur ibne-Maja."
2952,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''(janwer ke) paaon se honey wala nuqsan zaya hai (us ka koi moawza nahin).'' aur farmaya : ''aag (kisi ne apni jagah mein aag jalaaii, aur phir aandhi us aag ko uda kar kisi aur jagah ley gaee aur wahan aag lag gaee to us) ka nuqsan hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
2953,"Hazrat Hasan, Samura (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi janwaron ke paas aaye aur agar wahan unke Malik ko paey to us se ijazat talab karey aur agar wo wahan na ho to teen dafa aawaz dey , agar koi shakhs usey jawab dey to us se ijazat talab karey aur agar koi usey jawab na dey to wo khud doodh dho kar pi ley lekin wo apney sath na laye.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
2954,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu), Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs kisi baagh mein jaey to zarurat ke tehat wahan se kha ley lekin kapdey mein dal kar sath na laye.'' Tirmizi, ibne-Maja. Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi aur ibne-Maja."
2955,"Hazrat Umayya bin Sawaan apney walid se riwayat kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ghazwae-Hunain ke moqe par us se kuchh zarreen udhaar lein to usney kaha : Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ! ghasab ke taur par lena chahtey ho? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''nahin, balke qabile-wapsi , udhaar ke taur par.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
2956,"Hazrat Abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''udhaar'' li hui chiz wapis ki jaey, ata ke taur par mili hui chiz (doodh deney wala janwer) wapis lota di jaey, qarz ada kiya jaey aur zaamin tawaan (jurmana) bharney wala hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi aur Abu-Dawood."
2957,"Hazrat Raafe bin Amr Ghifaari (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main chhota sa ladka tha aur main ansaar ke khajuron ke darakhton par patthar phenk raha tha, to mujhey (pakad kar) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas laya gaya. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ladkey ! tum ne khajoor ke darakhton par patthar kyon phenkey?'' maine arz kiya, khajuren khaney ke liye, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''patthar na maaro , jo nichey giri hon un mein se khaao.'' phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne merey sar par shafqat se haath phera aur dua ki : ''aey Allah ! iskey pet ko bhar dey.'' rawahu Tirmizi, Abu-Dawood, ibne-Maja . ( وَسَنَذْکُرُ حَدِیْثَ عَمْرِ وبْنِ شُعَیْبِ فِیْ بَابِ اللُّقْطَۃِ اِنْ شَاءَ اللہُ تَعَالیٰ ) aur Amr bin Shuaib ki hadees ko ham انشاءاللہ  baab ''اللقطۃ'' mein zikr karengey."
2958,"Hazrat Salim apney walid se riwayat kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs thodi si bhi zamin nahaq wasul kerega to roze-qiyamat usey saat zaminon tak dhansa diya jaeyga.'' Bukhari."
2959,"Hazrat Yala bin Murra (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''jo shakhs nahaq kuchh zamin hasil karta hai to usey hukm diya jaeyga ke wo hashr ke maidan mein uski mitti uthaey rakhey.'' rawahu Ahmed."
2960,"Hazrat Yala bin Murra (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''jis shakhs ne nahaq baalisht barabar zamin par qabza kiya to Allah  usey hukm dega ke saton zaminon tak usey khodey , phir roze-qiyamat tak , yahan tak ke logon ke darmiyan faisla ho janey tak , usey uska toq pehna diya jaeyga.'' rawahu Ahmed."
2961,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ghair munqasim (bati hui) chiz ke mutalliq Shufaa ka faisla farmaya , aur jab had bandi ho jaey aur raastey mukhtalif ho jaeyn to phir koi Shufaa nahin.'' Bukhari."
2962,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ghair munqasim (bati hui) her mushtarka chiz mein Shufaa ka faisla diya, wo makaan ho ya baagh : ''us shakhs ke liye jayez nahin ke wo apney sharaakat daar ko ittilaa kiye baghair usey farokht kar dey , phir agar wo chahey to le-ley aur agar chahey to tarak kar dey , phir agar wo farokht kartey waqt usey ittilaa na karey to wo (doosra sharaakat daar) uska ziyada haq daar hai.'' rawahu Muslim."
2963,"Hazrat Abu-Raafe (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''padosi apney qurb ki wajeh se (Shufaa ka ( ziyada haq daar hai.'' Bukhari."
2964,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''padosi apney padosi ko apni deewar par shehteer rakhney se mana na karey.'' muttafaq aleh."
2965,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab raastey (ke arz) ke barey main tumhara ikhtilaf ho jaey to phir uska arz saat haath rakha jaeyga.'' rawahu Muslim."
2966,"Hazrat Saeed bin Hurais (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''tum mein se jo shakhs koi ghar ya koi zamin farokht karey to mumkin hai ke us (ki bai) ke liye barkat na rakhi jaey illa ye ke wo (raqam) ko isi tarah ki chiz mein lagaey.'' rawahu ibne-Maja aur Darmi."
2967,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''padosi apney Shufaa ka ziyada haq daar hai. agar wo kahin gaya hua hai to uska intizar kiya jaeyga jabkey un dono ka raasta eik hi ho.'' rawahu Ahmed, Tirmizi, Abu-Dawood, ibne-Maja aur Darmi."
2968,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''sharaakat daar Shufaa kar sakta hai aur Shufaa her chiz mein ho sakta hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
2969,Hazrat ibne-Abi Muleka ki sanad se Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se mursal marwi (bayan) hai aur wo ziyada sahih hai. انظر الحدیث السابق.
2970,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Hubaish (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs beri ka darkht kaat daley to Allah Taala usey sar ke bal jahannam mein daley ga.'' Abu-Dawood. aur farmaya : ye hadees mukhtasar hai, yani : ''jisney nahaq taur par kisi jangal se beri ka darkht kaat dala jiskey nichey musafir aur janwer saya hasil kartey hon, to Allah Taala usey sar ke bal jahannam mein daleyga.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
2971,"Hazrat Usman bin Affan (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab zamin ki hudood mutayyan (tai) ho jaeyn to phir is mein Shufaa nahin, aur isi tarah kuneyn aur pewand lagi khajoor mein Shufaa nahin. rawahu Malik."
2972,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne khaibar ke yahood ko khaibar ke nakhlistan aur uski zamin is shart par di ke wo apney amwaal (maalon) se in mein kaam karen, aur uski pedawar ka nisf (aadha) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke liye hoga. aur Sahih Bukhari ki riwayat mein hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne khaibar yahudiyon ko diya ke wo kaam karen aur kaasht kaari karen aur iski pedawar ka nisf unhen milega. rawahu Muslim Al Bukhari."
2973,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham mukhaabirat kiya kartey they aur ham is mein koi harj mehsus nahin kartey they, yahan tak ke Raafe bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne isey mana farmaya hai. lihaza ham ne is wajeh se tarak kar diya. rawahu Muslim."
2974,"Hazrat Hanzala bin Qais, Raafe bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain, merey do chacha Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke daur mein zamin kiraaey par diya kartey they, lekin wo barsaati naaley ke Aas paas ugney wali kheti ya koi aur chiz mustasna (alag) kar liya kartey they, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamein is se mana farma diya, maine Raafe (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha : wo dirham aur Dinar ke badley deney mein kya hukm rakhti hai? unhoney kaha : is mein koi harj nahin, aur jis wajeh se aisa karney se mana kiya gaya hai agar halal aur haram ke mutalliq jaan-ney wala sahab Faham aur samajhdaari se uska jayeza ley to wo bhi is mein mojud dhokey ke peshe-nazar isey jayez qarar na dey. muttafaq aleh."
2975,"Hazrat Raafe bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham ehle Madina ziyada tar kashtkar they, ham mein se koi apni zamin kiraaey par deta to yun kehta : ye zamin ka hissa mera hai aur ye tera, kabhi-kabhi ye hissey zamin ka pedawar deta , aur ye na deta , lihaza Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen mana farma diya. muttafaq aleh."
2976,"Hazrat Amr bayan kartey hain, maine Taaous se kaha : kaash! ke aap mukhaabira chhod den , kyonkey aam guman ye hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne is se mana farmaya hai, unhoney farmaya : Amr ! main unhen zamin deta hun aur unki madad bhi karta hun, aur be-shak un mein badey aalim yani ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujhey bataya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us se mana nahin farmaya : lekin aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar tum mein se koi apney bhai ko bator ehsan muft zamin dey dey to wo uskey liye moayan (taishuda) miqdaar mein ujrat leney se behtar hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
2977,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ki zamin ho to wo usey kaasht karey ya bator ehsan usey apney bhai ko dey dey , agar aisa nahin kar sakta to wo apni zamin apney paas rakhey.'' muttafaq aleh."
2978,"Hazrat Abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney hal ya koi khaiti ke auzaar dekhe to kaha : maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''kisi qom ke jis ghar mein ye chizen ghus aati hain, to Allah unhen zillat se dochaar kar deta hai.'' Bukhari."
2979,"Hazrat Raafe bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs kisi ki zamin mein unki ijazat ke baghair kaasht karey to kheti ki pedawar se usey kuchh nahin milega, wo sirf kharchey ka haqdaar hai.'' Tirmizi, Abu-Dawood. aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi aur Abu-Dawood."
2980,"Hazrat Qais bin Muslim, Abu-Jaafar se bayan kartey hain, tamam Muhajir Madina mein tihai ya chothai hissey par kheti kartey they, Ali , Saad bin Maalik , Abdullah bin Masood , umr bin Abdul-Azeez , Qasim , Urwa , aale Abu-Bakar , aale umr , aur aale Ali aur ibne Sireen ne kheti ki, aur Abdur-Rehman bin Aswad bayan kartey hain, main kheti mein Abdur-Rehman bin Yazid ke sath sharaakat kiya karta tha, aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne logon se maamla kiya ke agar umr beej mohaiyya kerega to nisf (aadhi) pedawar wo lega aur agar wo beej mohaiyya karengey to unke liye itna hissey hoga. Bukhari."
2981,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Mughaffal (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Sabit bin Suhak ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne muzaar'at (kheti) se mana farmaya aur muwajirat (thekey) par kaam karney ka hukm farmaya, aur farmaya : ''is mein koi harj nahin.'' rawahu Muslim."
2982,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne pachhney lagwaaey to pachhney laganey waley ko uski ujrat di aur naak mein dawaai dalwaai. muttafaq aleh.
2983,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ke her Nabi ne bakriyan charaai hain.'' aap ke Sahaba ne arz kiya : aapney bhi? farmaya : ''haan ! main bhi chand qiraat par Makka walon ki bakriyan charaaya karta tha.'' Bukhari."
2984,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah taala farmata hai : teen qism ke log aisey hain ke roze-qiyamat mein khud un se jhagdonga : eik wo aadmi jo mera naam lekar ehad karey phir usey tod daley , wo shakhs jo kisi azad aadmi ko bech kar uski qeemat kha jaey aur eik wo aadmi jo kisi mazdoor ko ujrat par rakhey to us se pura kaam ley lekin usey ujrat na dey.'' Bukhari."
2985,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke chand Sahaba ka pani (ke ghaat) ke paas se guzar hua to wahan eik aadmi tha jisey bichchhu ya sanp ne das liya tha, is pani par abaad logon mein se eik aadmi aaya to usney kaha : kya tum mein koi dam jhaad karney wala hai? kyonkey hamari abaadi main eik aadmi hai jisey bichchhu ya sanp ne das liya hai, un (Sahaba kiraam) mein se eik aadmi gaya aur kuchh bakriyon ke iwaz is par Sura Fatiha padhi aur bakriyan lekar apney sathiyon ke paas aaya to unhoney isey napasand kiya, aur kaha : kya tum ne Allah ki kitab par ujrat ley li? yahan tak ke wo Madina pahunch gaey, to unhoney arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! isney Allah ki kitab par ujrat li hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis chiz par tum ujrat leney ke sab se ziyada haq daar ho, wo Allah ki kitab hai.'' aur eik dusri hadees mein hai :  tum ne theek kiya, taqseem karo aur apney sath mera bhi hissey muqarrar karo.'' Bukhari."
2986,"Hazrat Khaarija bin Salat apney chacha se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha : ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas se wapis aa rahey they, to ham eik Arab qabiley ke paas aaye to unhoney kaha : hamein pata chala ke tum us aadmi se khair (yani Quran ( lekar aa rahey ho, kya tumharey paas koi dawaai ya dam hai kyonkey hamarey paas eik majnun shakhs jakdaa hua hai? ham ne kaha : haan , wo us jakdey huey deewaney ko ley aaye to maine teen roz subah aur Sham Sura Fatiha ka dam kiya, main apna thook (munh mein) jama kar leta phir usey (us majnun par) thook deta , raawi bayan kartey hain, uski bimari aur deewangi jati rahi to unhoney mujhey ujrat di to maine kaha padhi. nahin, (main isey nahin lunga) yahan tak ke main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se poochh lun, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''meri umr ki qism ! khaao , kuchh aisey hain jo jhootey dam ke zariey khatey hain, jabkey tum ne achey dam se khaya.'' rawahu Ahmed aur Abu-Dawood."
2987,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mazdoor ko uski ujrat , uska paseena khushk honey se pehley ada kar do.'' rawahu ibne-Maja."
2988,"Hazrat Husain bin Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''saail ka haq hai chaahe wo ghodey par aaye.'' Ahmed, Abu-Dawood. aur Masaabeh mein mursal riwayat hai, rawahu Ahmed aur Abu-Dawood."
2989,"Hazrat Utba bin munzir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir they ke aapney ''Sura Taa-Seen-Meem'' tilawat farmaai yahan tak ke aap Musa (Alaihissalam) ke qisse par pahunchey to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Musa (Alaihissalam) ne apni sharm-gah ki hifazat aur pet bharne ki khatir apney aap ko aath ya das saal mazduri par lagaey rakha.'' rawahu Ahmed aur ibne-Maja."
2990,"Hazrat Ubada bin Saamit (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! eik aadmi ne eik kamaan mujhey bator hadiya di hai aur ye isliye hai ke main usey kitab aur Quran ki taalim diya karta tha, aur wo koi maal nahin, main is se Allah ki raah mein teer andazi karunga , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar to pasand karta hai ke tujhey aag ka toq dal diya jaey to phir usey qubul kar ley.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood aur ibne-Maja."
2991,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat karti hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs kisi banjar (be-abaad) zamin ko, jo ke kisi ki milkiyat na ho, abaad karey to wo (uska) ziyada haq daar hai.'' Urwa bayan kartey hain, umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne apni khilaafat mein usi ke mutabiq faisla kiya. Bukhari."
2992,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Sa'ab bin Jasama (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''charaagaah to sirf Allah aur uskey Rasool ke liye hai.'' Bukhari."
2993,"Hazrat Urwa bayan kartey hain, Zuber ka Harra ke barsaati naaley main eik Ansari aadmi se jhagda ho gaya to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Zubair ! pehley tum sairab kar lo, phir apney padosi ke liye chhod do.'' Ansari bolney laga : kyonkey wo aap ki phuphi ka beta hai ! aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke chehrey ka rang tabdeel ho gaya, phir farmaya : ''Zubair ! pehley tum sairab karo, phir pani roke rakho yahan tak ke wo mundeer tak pahunch jaey, phir apney padosi ki taraf chhod dey.'' yun Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne sareeh hukm mein (haqiqat mein) Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ko pura haq dey diya. jabkey Ansari ne (qole-faisal par moa'tariz ho kar) aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko ghussa dilaayaa, halanke aapney pehley aisa hukm diya tha jis mein dono ke liye wusat (aasani) thi. muttafaq aleh."
2994,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''zarurat se zayada ghaas rokney ke liye zarurat se zayada pani mat roko.'' muttafaq aleh."
2995,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''teen shakhs aisey hain, jin se Allah roze-qiyamat kalam kerega na nazare-rehmat se unki taraf dekhega : wo aadmi jisney maal par qism uthai ho ke usey to us sey, jitni tum dey rahey ho, ziyada qeemat milti hai, halanke wo jhoota hai, doosra wo shakhs jo Asr ke baad jhooti qism uthaey taake uskey zariey kisi musalman shakhs ka maal harrap kar jaey, aur teesra wo shakhs jisney zarurat se zayada pani rok rakha ho, Allah farmaeyga : aaj mein tujhey apney Fazal se mehroom rakhunga jaisa ke to ne zarurat se zayada pani rok liya tha. halanke usey terey haathon ne nahin banaya tha.'' muttafaq aleh. (وَذْکِرَ حَدِیْثُ جَابِر padhi. فِیْ ’ ’ بَابِ الْمَنْھِیِّ عَنْھَا مِنَ الْبُیُوْع) aur Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ki riwayat (باب المنھی عنھا من البیوع) mein zikr ki ja chuki hai."
2996,"Hazrat Hasan (Raziallahu anhu) Samura (Raziallahu anhu) se aur wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs kisi (banjar) zamin par chaar diwaari kar ley to wo zamin ka hissa uska hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
2997,Hazrat Asma bin Abi Bakr (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ko jaagir mein kuchh khajuron ke darkht ata farmaey.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood.
2998,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ke liye unke ghodey ki daud tak masafat (doori) ka raqba jaagir mein ata kiya, unhoney apna ghoda daudaayaa yahan tak ke wo khada ho gaya. phir unhoney apna kodaa phenka , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jahan tak kodaa pahuncha hai wahan tak raqba usey ata kar do.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
2999,"Hazrat Alqama bin Waael apney walid se riwayat kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Hizre-Maut (Yamen) ke ilaqey mein unhen jaagir di, wo bayan kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ko merey sath bheja aur farmaya : ''wo unhen dey aao.'' rawahu Tirmizi aur Darmi."
3000,"Hazrat Abyaz bin Hammal Maarbi se riwayat hai ke wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaye to aap se Maarib ki namak ki kaan bator jaagir talab ki to aapney wo usey ata kar di, jab wo aadmi wapis muda to eik aadmi ne arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! aapney to usey daaimi chiz ata farma di, raawi bayan kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey us se wapis ley liya. raawi bayan kartey hain ke usney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se puchha peelu ke darakhton ki zamin kis qadr door ja kar gherli jaey? farmaya : '' jahan oont na pahunch paeyn.'' rawahu Tirmizi, ibne-Maja aur Darmi."
3001,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''musalman teen chizon : pani, ghaas aur aag mein, hisse daar hain.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood aur ibne-Maja."
3002,"Hazrat Ismar bin Muzarris (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to maine aap ki baiat ki, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs kisi aisey pani (chashmey) par, jahan koi musalman na pahuncha ho, pehley pahunch jaey to wo pani usi ka hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
3003,"Hazrat Taaus (Raziallahu anhu) se mursal riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs banjar zamin ko abaad kar ley to wo usi ki hai. aur qadim (puraani) banjar zamin Allah aur uskey Rasool ki hai, phir wo meri taraf se tumharey liye hai.'' rawahu Shafai."
3004,"Hazrat Sharahus-Sunnah mein marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ko Madina mein kuchh ghar bator jaagir ata kiye, wo ansaar ke gharon aur nakhlistan ke darmiyan they, banu-Abd bin Zohra ne kaha : ibne Umme-Abd ( Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu)) ko ham se door kar den, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen farmaya : ''tab Allah ne mujhey mab-us (bheja) hi kyon kiya hai, be-shak Allah is ummat ko paak nahin karta jis mein unke zaeef shakhs ko uska haq na dilaaya jaey.'' (rawahu fi Sharahus-Sunnah)."
3005,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib apney walid se aur wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne seel mahzor ke barey mein faisla farmaya ke usko roka jaey yahan tak ke wo (pani) takhnon tak pahunch jaey, phir baalai (upri) hissey se nashebi (nichle) hissey ko pani chhoda jaey. rawahu Abu-Dawood aur ibne-Maja."
3006,"Hazrat Samura bin Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unke khajuron ke kuchh darkht eik Ansari shakhs ke baagh mein they, aur uskey bachchey bhi us shakhs ke sath (baagh mein) they, Samura (Raziallahu anhu) jab us shakhs ke paas jatey to wo un se takleef mehsus karta, wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur aap ko sari baat batai to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Samura (Raziallahu anhu) ko apney paas bulaya taake wo usey farokht kar den lekin unhoney inkar kar diya, aapney mutalba kiya ke un darakhton ke badla mein kisi aur jagah leylo, lekin unhoney inkar kar diya, farmaya : ''usey hiba kar do.'' aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne targheeb ke andaz mein farmaya ke : ''tumhen (jannat mein) ye kuchh milega.'' unhoney phir bhi inkar kar diya, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum takleef pahunchaney waley ho.'' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Ansari shakhs se farmaya : ''jaao aur uskey khajuron ke darkht kaat do.'' aur Jabir se marwi (bayan) hadees : ''jisney banjar zamin ko abaad kiya.'' Saeed bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ki riwayat se (باب الغصب) mein zikr ki gaee hai. aur ham Abu-Sarma (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hadees : ''jisney kisi ko takleef pahunchaai to Allah usey takleef pahunchaeyga.''  (باب ما ینھی an التھاجر) main zikr karengey. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
3007,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke unhoney arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! wo kon si chiz hai jis ka rokna halal nahin? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''pani, namak aur aag.'' wo bayan karti hain, maine arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! pani ki ahmiyat aur zarurat ka to hamein pata hai, lekin namak aur aag ki to wo surat nahin hai. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Humeraa ! jis shakhs ne aag di to goya usney us aag se pakney wali tamam chizen , sadqa kin. aur jisney namak diya to goya us namak ne jin chizon ko lazeez banaya wo tamam chizen usney sadqa kin. jis shakhs ne pani ke hotey huey kisi musalman ko eik ghoont pani pilaya to goya usney eik ghulam azad kiya, aur jisney pani ki adam dastyaabi (na milne) ki surat mein kisi musalman ko pani ka ghoont pila diya to goya usney usey zindagi ata kar di.'' rawahu ibne-Maja."
3008,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke khaibar ki kuchh zamin umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke hissey mein aai to unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! mujhey khaibar ki jo zamin mili hai is-se pehley itna nafis (badhiya) maal mujhey kabhi nahin mila, aap iskey mutalliq mujhey kya hukm farmatey hain? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar tum chaho to uska asal maal tum rakh lo aur uski pedawar sadqa kar do.'' umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne is shart par usey sadqa kiya ke uskey asal ko bechaa jaeyga na hiba kiya jaeyga aur na hi virasat mein taqseem hoga aur uski pedawar ko fuqaraa, rishte-daaron, ghulamon ko azad karaaney, Allah ki raah mein , musafir par aur mehmano par kharch kiya jaeyga, aur uski sarparasti aur nigrani karney waley par is baat mein koi gunah nahin ke wo is mein se bhaley tareeqey se khaye zakhira na kartey huey dusron (ehle khana waghera) ko bhi khilaaey.'' ibne Sireeen (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : maal jama karney wala na ho. muttafaq aleh."
3009,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''umraa (umar bhar ka atiya)  jayez hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
3010,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''umraa (umar bhar ka atiya), umra leney waley warison ki meeras hai.'' rawahu Muslim."
3011,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs aur uski aulad ko umraa (umar bhar ka atiya) diya gaya to wo unhi ka hai jin ko diya gaya, wo deney waley ko wapis nahin hoga, kyonkey usney eik aisa Atiya diya hai jis mein meeras waqey ho gaee hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
3012,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, umraa (umar bhar ka atiya) jisey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne nafiz kiya hai wo ye hai ke koi shakhs kahe : ye (umraa) tumharey aur tumhari aulad ke liye hai, aur agar wo kahey ke jab tak to zinda rahey ye chiz teri hai, to phir (us ki wafat ke baad) ye uskey Malik ko wapis mil jaeygi.'' muttafaq aleh."
3013,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum raqba ke taur par koi chiz do na umra (umar bhar ka atiya) ke taur par , jis shakhs ko raqba ke taur par koi chiz di gaee ya umra ke taur par to wo uskey warison ki hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
3014,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''umraa , jis shakhs ko umra diya jaey uskey ehle khana ke liye nafiz hoga aur ruqbaa , jis shakhs ko ruqbaa diya jaey wo uskey ehle khana ke liye nafiz hoga.'' rawahu Ahmed, Tirmizi aur Abu-Dawood."
3015,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''apney amwaal ki hifazat karo aur unhen kharab na karo, kyonkey jis shakhs ne umraa (umar bhar ka atiya) diya to wo usi shakhs ka hai jis ko umra diya gaya uski zindagi mein bhi, uskey marney ke baad bhi aur uskey wirsa ka hai.'' rawahu Muslim."
3016,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ko khushbu pesh ki jaey to wo usey wapis na karey kyonkey wo halka sa ehsan aur achhi khushbu hai.'' rawahu Muslim."
3017,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasool karim (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khushbu (ke tohfey) ko wapis nahin kiya kartey they. Bukhari.
3018,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''hiba wapis leney wala, qai karkey usey chaatney waley kuttey ki tarah hai. hamarey liye buri misal nahin?'' Bukhari ."
3019,"Hazrat Noman bin Bashir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke merey walid mujhey lekar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey to arz kiya, maine apney bete ko eik ghulam hiba kiya hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tum ne apni sari aulad ko (barabar) is tarah ka hiba kiya hai? '' unhoney arz kiya, nahin, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usey wapis ley lo.'' eik dusri riwayat mein hai ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tum pasand kartey ho ke wo sarey terey sath masaawi barabar Husane sulook keren?'' unhoney arz kiya : ji haan ! aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' to phir tum aisey kyon nahin kartey?'' eik riwayat mein hai, unhoney kaha : merey walid ne mujhey eik Atiya diya to Umra binte Rawaha (Raziallahu anhu) (meri walida) ne kaha : main razi nahin yahan tak ke tum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko gawah bana lo. wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaye to arz kiya : maine Umra binte Rawaha (Raziallahu anhu) se apney bete ko eik Atiya diya hai aur Allah ke Rasool ! usney kaha hai ke main aap ko gawah banaun. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tum ne apni baqi aulad ko bhi isi tarah ka Atiya diya hai? '' unhoney arz kiya nahin, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah se daro aur apni aulad ke darmiyan insaf karo.'' raawi bayan kartey hain, wo wapis aaye aur apna Atiya wapis ley liya . aur eik dusri riwayat mein hai : ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main zulm par gawah nahin banta.'' muttafaq aleh."
3020,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''koi shakhs hiba karkey wapis nahin ley sakta, albatta waliden apni aulad ko koi chiz hiba karkey wapis ley saktey hain.'' rawahu Nasai aur ibne-Maja."
3021,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) aur ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' kisi aadmi ke liye halal nahin ke wo Atiya de-kar wapis ley, magar walid jo apni aulad ko Atiya deta hai, aur us shakhs ki misal jo Atiya de-kar wapis ley kuttey ki tarah hai jo khata rehta hai, yahan tak ke pet bhar jata hai to qai kar deta hai, phir usey khaney lagta hai.'' Abu-Dawud, Tirmizi, Nasai , ibne-Maja . aur Imam Tirmizi ne isey sahih qarar diya hai. rawahu Abu-Dawood, Tirmizi, Nasai aur ibne-Maja."
3022,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik Erabi (dehati) (dehaati) ne eik nau-umar oont Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko bator hadiya pesh kiya to aapney uskey iwaz usey chhe nau-umar oontniyaan den, lekin wo razi na hua . jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko uska pata chala to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Allah ki hamd aur sanaa bayan ki, phir farmaya : ''falan shakhs ne mujhey eik oont bator hadiya pesh kiya to maine uskey iwaz usey chhe oontniyaan den lekin wo phir bhi razi nahin hua. ab maine azm (iraada) kar liya hai ke main sirf kisi Quraishi , Ansari , Saqafi ya dosi shakhs ka hadiya hi qubul karunga.'' rawahu Tirmizi, Abu-Dawood aur Nasai ."
3023,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ko koi Atiya diya jaey aur wo kashaaish (kushadgi) paey to uska badla dey aur jo shakhs kashaaish na paey to wo uski tareef karey, kyonkey jisney tareef ki to usney shukriya ada kiya, aur jisney (ehsan ko) chupaya to usney nashukri ki, aur jo shakhs aisi chiz zahir karney ki koshish karey jo usey nahin di gaee to wo jhoot ke do soot pehanney waley ki tarah hai (dohra jhoot bolney waley ki tarah hai).'' rawahu Tirmizi aur Abu-Dawood."
3024,"Hazrat Usama bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jiskey sath koi bhalai ki gaee aur usney bhalai karney waley se kaha :(جَزَاکَ اللہُ خَیْرًا)  ''Allah tumhen behtar badla dey'' to usney uski bahut achhi tareef ki.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
3025,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jisney logon ka shukriya ada na kiya, usney Allah ka bhi shukriya ada na kiya.'' rawahu Ahmed aur Tirmizi."
3026,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Madina tashrif laye to Muhajir Sahaba kiram aap ke paas aaye aur arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! ham jis qom ke yahan qiyam pazeer (thehre hue) hain wo maal Kasir (ziyada) honey ki surat mein bahut ziyada kharch karney waley aur maal qaleel (kam) honey ki surat mein behtareen gham khuwar honey main apni misal nahin rakhtey , unhoney hamein kaam karney se roke rakha hai aur munfa'at (nafe) mein barabar shareek kar rakha hai. yahan tak ke hamein to andesha hai ke sara ajr wohi ley jaeyngey, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tak tum unke liye Allah se duayen kartey rahogey aur unki tareef kartey rahogey to aisey nahin hoga.'' Tirmizi, aur unhoney isey sahih qarar diya hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
3027,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat karti hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''baham (aapas mein) tohfe diya karo, kyonkey tohfa adawat door kar deta hai.''"
3028,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''baham (aapas mein) tohfe diya karo, kyonkey tohfa seeney ka keena door kar deta hai, aur padausan apni padausan ke hadiya ko maamuli na samjhey chahey (chaahe) bakri ke khur ka eik hissey hi ho.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
3029,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''teen chizen wapis nahin ki jaani chaahein, takiya, tel aur doodh. Tirmizi aur farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. kaha gaya ke tel se khushbu murad hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
3030,"Hazrat Abu-Usman Nahdi (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se kisi shakhs ko khushbu pesh ki jaey to wo usey wapis na karey, kyonkey wo jannat se aai hai.'' Tirmizi, riwayat mursal hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
3031,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Bashir (Raziallahu anhu) ki ehliya ne kaha : merey bete ko apna ghulam hiba kar do aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko is par gawah banaao. wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaye to arz kiya : falan ki beti (yani meri ehliya) ne mujh se mutalba kiya hai ke main uskey bete ko apna ghulam hiba karun aur usney ye bhi kaha hai ke is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko gawah banaun, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''iskey aur bhi bhai hain?'' unhoney arz kiya, ji haan ! aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tum ne jo us ladkey ko diya hai wo un sab ko bhi diya hai? '' unhoney arz kiya, nahin, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye to munasib nahin, aur main to sirf haq baat par hi gawahi deta hun.'' rawahu Muslim."
3032,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke jab pehla pehla phal aap ki khidmat mein pesh kiya jata to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) usey apni aakhon aur honton par lagatey aur dua farmatey : ''aey Allah ! jis tarah to ne hamein iska aaghaz dikhaya hai isi tarah hamen uska ikhtitaam bhi dikhaanaa. phir aap usey apney paas bethey huey kisi bachchey ko dey detey . (rawahu al-Behaqi fi الدعوات الکبیر )."
3033,"Hazrat Zaid bin Khalid (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik aadmi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to usney aap se giri padi ya khoee hui cheez ke barey mein puchha to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' us (milney wali chiz) ki thaili aur usey baandhney wali rassi ki pehchan rakh, phir eik saal tak uska aelan kar, agar uska maalik aa jaey to theek warna to usey apney istimal mein ley aa .'' usney gum shuda bakri ke barey mein masla puchha to farmaya : '' (usey pakad ley) wo terey liye hai ya terey kisi bhai ke liye ya phir bhediye ke liye.'' usney gum shuda oont ke barey mein sawal kiya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tujhey us se kya sarokaar? (pani ka ( mishkeeza uskey paas aur paaon uskey mazbut hain (piyas lagney par) ghaat par aaeyga aur darkht ke pattey khayega yahan tak ke uska maalik us tak pahunch jaeyga.'' muttafaq aleh. aur Muslim ki riwayat mein hai : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''eik saal tak uska aelan kar. phir us chiz ko baandhney wali rassi aur uski thaili ki pehchan rakh, phir usey istimal mein la. albatta agar uska maalik aa jaey to phir usey itni qeemat ada kar.''"
3034,"Hazrat Zaid bin Khalid (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs kisi gum shuda chiz ko panah dey aur uska aelan na karey to wo khud gumrah hai.'' rawahu Muslim."
3035,Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Usman Taimi (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hajiyon ki giri padi chiz uthaney se mana farmaya. rawahu Muslim.
3036,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib apney walid se aur wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain, aur unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kiya ke aap se darkht par latkey huey phal ke mutalliq puchha gaya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar koi zarurat mand shakhs, jo ke kapdey mein dal kar ley janey wala na ho, wahan se kha ley to is par koi muwaakhiza (pakad/gunah) nahin, aur jo shakhs wahan se kuchh sath ley aaye to is par do-guna jurmana aur saza hai, aur jo shakhs jins ke dher lag janey ke baad wahan se dhaal ki qeemat ke barabar chori karey to uska haath kaataa jaeyga.'' aur gum shuda oont aur gum shuda bakri ke barey mein bhi dusri chizon ki tarah hi zikr kiya gaya hai. raawi bayan kartey hain, aap se giri padi ya khoee hui cheez ke barey mein sawal kiya gaya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar wo shaarea' aam aur badi basti se miley to phir to eik saal tak uska aelan kar , agar uska maalik aa jaey to wo uskey hawaley kar , aur agar koi maalik na aaye to phir wo teri hai. aur agar wo kisi be-abaad qadim (purani) jagah se miley to phir is mein aur madfun (dabe hue) Khazeeney mein paanchwan hissey hai.'' Nasai . Abu-Dawood (Raziallahu anhu) ne bhi unhi se riwayat kiya hai aur wo hadees : (سُئِلَ عَنِ اللُّقْطَۃِ ( se aakhir tak marwi (bayan) hai. rawahu Nasai aur Abu-Dawood."
3037,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Ali bin Abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) ko eik Dinar mila wo usey Fatima (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas ley aaye aur is barey mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se masla puchha to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye to Allah ka rizq hai.'' Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) , Ali (Raziallahu anhu) aur Fatima (Raziallahu anhu) ne is mein se khaya. jab aglaa roz hua to eik aurat Dinar ka aelan karti hui aai to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Ali ! Dinar wapis karo.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
3038,"Hazrat Jaarud (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''musalman ki gum shuda chiz (agar wo aelan kiye baghair utha li jaey to wo) aag ka shola hai.'' rawahu Darmi."
3039,"Hazrat Ayaaz bin Himaar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs giri padi chiz pa ley to wo eik ya do aadil shakhs gawah bana ley . aur wo usey chupaey na usey ghayeb karey, agar uska maalik pa ley to wo chiz usey wapis karey warna wo Allah ka maal hai jisey chahta hai ata karta hai.'' rawahu Ahmed aur Abu-Dawood aur Darmi."
3040,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne lathi, kodey, rassi aur us se milti jalti chizon ke barey mein hamein rukhsat (choot) inayat farmaai ke aadmi is tarah ki giri padi chiz ko utha kar istimal kar ley. rawahu Abu-Dawood. (وَذْکِرَ حَدِیْثُ الْمِقْدَامِ بْنِ مَعْدِیْ کَرِبَ : ( اَلَا لَا یَحِلُّ ( فِیْ بَابِ الاعْعِصَامِ) aur Miqdam bin Maadi Karb (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hadees (اَلَا لَا یَحِلُّ . . . . .) باب الاعتصام mein zikr ki gaee hai."
